nemsio_openclose.f90

1 !----------------------------------------------------------------------------
2 module nemsio_openclose
3 !
4 !$$$ documentation clock
5 !
6 ! module: nemsio_openclose Open and close a nemsio file
7 ! Programmer: J. Wang date: 2011-01-13
8 !
9 ! abstract: this module provides subroutines to open or close a nemsio file.
10 ! A data type that contains all the header information in the file
11 ! is provided, this data structure has 12 standard meta data records
12 ! as well as user-defined meta data. subroutine nemsio_getfilehead
13 ! is used to get elements for the standard metadata, while subroutine
14 ! nemsio_getheadvar could get one variable out from user-defined meta
15 ! data.
16 !
17 ! Possible return code
18 ! 0 Successful call
19 ! -1 Open or close I/O error
20 ! -2 array size inconsistent in gfile
21 ! -3 error in reading/write Meta data
22 ! -5 Search record or set GRIB message header (pds/gds) error
23 ! -6 allocate/deallocate error
24 ! -7 set grib table
25 ! -8 file meta data initialization (default:1152*576)
26 ! -9 NOT nemsio type file
27 ! -10 get/close file unit
28 ! -11 get field name, levtyp and lev from record number
29 ! -17 get var from file header
30 !
31 ! Public Defined Types
32 ! nemsio_gfile
33 ! private
34 ! gtype: character(nemsio_charkind8) NEMSIO file identifier
35 ! gdatatype:character(nemsio_charkind8) data format
36 ! modelname:character(nemsio_charkind8) modelname
37 ! version: integer(nemsio_intkind) verion number
38 ! nmeta: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of metadata rec
39 ! lmeta: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of metadata rec 2 for model paramodels
40 ! nrec: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of data rec
41 ! idate(1:7):integer(nemsio_intkind) initial date (yyyy/mm/dd/hh/mm/ssn/ssd)
42 ! nfday: integer(nemsio_intkind) forecast day
43 ! nfhour: integer(nemsio_intkind) forecast hour
44 ! nfminute:integer(nemsio_intkind) forecast minutes
45 ! nfsecondn:integer(nemsio_intkind) numerator of forecast second fraction
46 ! nfsecondd:integer(nemsio_intkind) denominator of forecast second fraction
47 ! dimy: integer(nemsio_intkind) dimension in latitude
48 ! dimx: integer(nemsio_intkind) dimension in Longitude
49 ! dimz: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of levels
50 ! nframe: integer(nemsio_intkind) dimension of halo
51 ! nsoil: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of soil layers
52 ! ntrac: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of tracers
53 ! jcap: integer(nemsio_intkind) spectral truncation
54 ! ncldt: integer(nemsio_intkind) number of cloud types
55 ! idsl: integer(nemsio_intkind) semi-lagrangian id
56 ! idvc: integer(nemsio_intkind) vertical coordinate id
57 ! idvm: integer(nemsio_intkind) mass variable id
58 ! idrt: integer(nemsio_intkind) grid identifier
59 ! (idrt=4 for gaussian grid,
60 ! idrt=0 for equally-spaced grid including poles,
61 ! idrt=256 for equally-spaced grid excluding poles)
62 ! rlon_min:real(nemsio_realkind) minimal longtitude of regional domain (global:set to 0)
63 ! rlon_max:real(nemsio_realkind) maximal longtitude of regional domain (global:set to 360.)
64 ! rlat_min:real(nemsio_realkind) minimal longtitude of regional domain (global:set to -90)
65 ! rlat_max:real(nemsio_realkind) maximal longtitude of regional domain (global:set to 90)
66 ! extrameta:logical(nemsio_logickind)extra meta data flag
67 ! nmetavari:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data integer variables
68 ! nmetavarr:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data real(4) variables
69 ! nmetavarl:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data logical variables
70 ! nmetavarc:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data character variables
71 ! nmetavarr8:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data real(8) variables
72 ! nmetaaryi:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data integer arrays
73 ! nmetaaryr:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data real(4) arrays
74 ! nmetaaryl:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data logical arrays
75 ! nmetaaryc:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data character arrays
76 ! nmetaaryr8:integer(nemsio_intkind) number of extra meta data real(8) arrays
77 !
78 ! recname: character(nemsio_charkind),allocatable recname(nrec) data field names
79 ! reclevtyp: character(nemsio_charkind),allocatable reclevtyp(nrec) data field level type
80 ! reclev: integer(nemsio_intkind),allocatable reclev(nrec) data field level
81 ! vcoord: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable vcoord(dimz+1,3,2) vertical coordinate
82 ! lat: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable lat(fieldsize) lat for mess point
83 ! lon: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable lon(fieldsize) lon for mess point
84 ! dx: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable dx(fieldsize) grid distance in x dimension
85 ! dy: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable dy(fieldsize) grid distance in y dimension
86 ! Cpi: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable cpi(ntracer+1)
87 ! specific heat at constant pressure,dryair + tracers
88 ! Ri: real(nemsio_realkind),allocatable ri(ntrac+1)
89 ! gas constant for dryair + tracers
90 !
91 ! variname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data integer variables
92 ! varrname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data real(4) variables
93 ! varlname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data logical variables
94 ! varcname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data string variables
95 ! varr8name:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data real(8) variables
96 ! varival: integer(nemsio_intkind) values of extra meta data integer variables
97 ! varrval: real(nemsio_realkind) values of extra meta data real(4) variables
98 ! varlval: logical(nemsio_logickind) values of extra meta data logical variables
99 ! varcval: character(nemsio_charkind) values of extra meta data string variables
100 ! varr8val: real(nemsio_dblekind) values of extra meta data real(8) variables
101 ! aryiname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data integer arrays
102 ! aryrname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data real arrays
103 ! aryr8name:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data real(8) arrays
104 ! arylname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data logical arrays
105 ! arycname:character(nemsio_charkind) names of extra meta data character arrays
106 ! aryilen: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of extra meta data integer arrays
107 ! aryrlen: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of extra meta data real(4) arrays
108 ! aryr8len: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of extra meta data real(8) arrays
109 ! aryllen: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of extra meta data logical arrays
110 ! aryclen: integer(nemsio_intkind) length of extra meta data string arrays
111 ! aryival: integer(nemsio_intkind) values of extra meta data integer arrays
112 ! aryrval: real(nemsio_realkind) values of extra meta data real(4) arrays
113 ! aryr8val: real(nemsio_dblekind) values of extra meta data real(8) arrays
114 ! arylval: logical(nemsio_logickind) values of extra meta data logical arrays
115 ! arycval: character(nemsio_charkind) values of extra meta data character arrays
116 !
117 ! gfname: character(255) file name
118 ! gaction: character(nemsio_charkind) read/write
119 ! flunit: integer(nemsio_intkind) unit number
120 ! tlmeta: integer(nemsio_intkind) total header length
121 ! fieldsize: integer(nemsio_intkind) size for one field
122 ! tlmetalat: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record lat
123 ! tlmetalon: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record lon
124 ! tlmetadx: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record dx
125 ! tlmetady: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record dy
126 ! tlmetavarival: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record varival
127 ! tlmetaaryival: integer(nemsio_intkind8) header length before header record aryival
128 ! file_endian: character(nemsio_charkind) file endianness
129 !
130 !Public subroutines:
131 !
132 ! nemsio_init
133 ! nemsio_finalize
134 ! nemsio_open
135 ! nemsio_close
136 ! nemsio_getfilehead
137 ! nemsio_getrechead
138 ! nemsio_getheadvar
139 ! nemsio_setheadvar
140 ! nemsio_setfilehead
141 !
142 !
143 !$$$ end documentation clock

385 contains
386 !-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
387  subroutine nemsio_init(iret)
388 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
389 ! initialization
390 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
391  implicit none
392  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out):: iret
393  integer :: ios
394 !------------------------------------------------------------
395 ! abstract: set grib table
396 !------------------------------------------------------------
397  call nemsio_setgrbtbl(ios)
398  if ( present(iret)) iret=ios
399  if ( ios.ne.0) then
400  if (present(iret)) return
401  call nemsio_stop
402  endif
403 !------------------------------------------------------------
404 ! check machine endian
405 !------------------------------------------------------------
406  call chk_endianc(machine_endian)
407  if(trim(machine_endian)=='mixed_endian') then
408  print *,'WARNING: You are in mixed endian computer!!!'
409  endif
410 !
411  end subroutine nemsio_init
412 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
413  subroutine nemsio_finalize()
414 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
415 ! abstract: finalization
416 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
417  implicit none
418 
419  end subroutine nemsio_finalize
420 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
421  subroutine nemsio_open(gfile,gfname,gaction,iret,gdatatype,version, &
422  nmeta,lmeta,modelname,nrec,idate,nfday,nfhour, &
423  nfminute,nfsecondn,nfsecondd, &
424  dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe,nsoil,ntrac,jcap,ncldt,idvc,idsl,idvm,idrt, &
425  rlon_min,rlon_max,rlat_min,rlat_max,extrameta, &
426  nmetavari,nmetavarr,nmetavarl,nmetavarc, &
427  nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl,nmetaaryc, &
428  nmetavarr8,nmetaaryr8, &
429  recname,reclevtyp,reclev,vcoord,lat,lon,dx,dy,cpi,ri, &
430  variname,varival,varrname,varrval,varlname,varlval,varcname,varcval, &
431  varr8name,varr8val, &
432  aryiname,aryilen,aryival,aryrname,aryrlen,aryrval, &
433  arylname,aryllen,arylval,arycname,aryclen,arycval, &
434  aryr8name,aryr8len,aryr8val )
435 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
436 ! abstract: open nemsio file, and read/write the meta data
437 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
438  implicit none
439  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
440  character*(*),intent(in) :: gfname
441  character*(*),intent(in) :: gaction
442 !-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
443 ! optional variables
444 !-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
445  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
446  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: gdatatype,modelname
447  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: version,nmeta,lmeta,nrec
448  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: idate(7),nfday,nfhour, &
449  nfminute, nfsecondn,nfsecondd
450  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe, &
451  nsoil,ntrac
452  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: jcap,ncldt,idvc,idsl, &
453  idvm,idrt
454  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: rlat_min,rlat_max, &
455  rlon_min,rlon_max
456  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(in):: extrameta
457  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: nmetavari,nmetavarr, &
458  nmetavarl,nmetavarc,nmetavarr8,nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl,&
459  nmetaaryc,nmetaaryr8
460 !
461  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: recname(:),reclevtyp(:)
462  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: reclev(:)
463  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: vcoord(:,:,:)
464  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: lat(:),lon(:)
465  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: dx(:),dy(:)
466  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: cpi(:),ri(:)
467 !
468  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: variname(:),varrname(:),&
469  varlname(:),varcname(:),varr8name(:),aryiname(:),aryrname(:), &
470  arylname(:),arycname(:),aryr8name(:)
471  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: aryilen(:),aryrlen(:), &
472  aryllen(:),aryclen(:),aryr8len(:)
473  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: varival(:),aryival(:,:)
474  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: varrval(:),aryrval(:,:)
475  real(nemsio_dblekind),optional,intent(in) :: varr8val(:),aryr8val(:,:)
476  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(in):: varlval(:),arylval(:,:)
477  character(*),optional,intent(in) :: varcval(:),arycval(:,:)
478 !
479  integer(nemsio_intkind) :: ios
480 !------------------------------------------------------------
481 ! assign a unit number
482 !------------------------------------------------------------
483  if (present(iret)) iret=-1
484  call nemsio_getlu(gfile,gfname,gaction,ios)
485  if ( ios.ne.0 ) then
486  if ( present(iret)) then
487  iret=ios
488  return
489  else
490  call nemsio_stop
491  endif
492  endif
493 !------------------------------------------------------------
494 ! open and read meta data for READ
495 !------------------------------------------------------------
496 ! print *,'in rcreate, gfname=',gfname,'gaction=',lowercase(gaction)
497  gfile%gfname=gfname
498  gfile%gaction=gaction
499  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'read') .or. equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'rdwr')) then
500  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'read') )then
501  call baopenr(gfile%flunit,gfname,ios)
502  if ( ios.ne.0) then
503  if ( present(iret)) then
504  return
505  else
506  call nemsio_stop
507  endif
508  endif
509  else
510  call baopen(gfile%flunit,gfname,ios)
511  if ( ios.ne.0) then
512  if ( present(iret)) then
513  return
514  else
515  call nemsio_stop
516  endif
517  endif
518  endif
519 !
520 ! read meta data for gfile
521 !
522  call nemsio_rcreate(gfile,gfname,gaction,ios)
523  if ( ios.ne.0) then
524  if ( present(iret)) then
525  iret=ios
526  return
527  else
528  call nemsio_stop
529  endif
530  endif
531 !
532 ! open and write meta data for WRITE
533 !------------------------------------------------------------
534  elseif ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'write') ) then
535  call baopenwt(gfile%flunit,gfname,ios)
536  if ( ios.ne.0) then
537  if ( present(iret)) then
538  return
539  else
540  call nemsio_stop
541  endif
542  endif
543  call nemsio_wcreate(gfile,gfname,gaction,ios,gdatatype=gdatatype, &
544  version=version, nmeta=nmeta,lmeta=lmeta,modelname=modelname, &
545  nrec=nrec,idate=idate,nfday=nfday,nfhour=nfhour, &
546  nfminute=nfminute,nfsecondn=nfsecondn, nfsecondd=nfsecondd, &
547  dimx=dimx,dimy=dimy,dimz=dimz,nframe=nframe,nsoil=nsoil, &
548  ntrac=ntrac,jcap=jcap,ncldt=ncldt,idvc=idvc,idsl=idsl, &
549  idvm=idvm,idrt=idrt, rlon_min=rlon_min,rlon_max=rlon_max, &
550  rlat_min=rlat_min, rlat_max=rlat_max,extrameta=extrameta, &
551  nmetavari=nmetavari,nmetavarr=nmetavarr,nmetavarr8=nmetavarr8,&
552  nmetavarl=nmetavarl, nmetavarc=nmetavarc,nmetaaryi=nmetaaryi, &
553  nmetaaryr=nmetaaryr, nmetaaryr8=nmetaaryr8, &
554  nmetaaryl=nmetaaryl,nmetaaryc=nmetaaryc,recname=recname, &
555  reclevtyp=reclevtyp,reclev=reclev,vcoord=vcoord, &
556  lat=lat,lon=lon,dx=dx,dy=dy,cpi=cpi,ri=ri, &
557  variname=variname,varival=varival,varrname=varrname, &
558  varrval=varrval,varlname=varlname,varlval=varlval, &
559  varcname=varcname,varcval=varcval, &
560  varr8name=varr8name,varr8val=varr8val, &
561  aryiname=aryiname,aryilen=aryilen,aryival=aryival, &
562  aryrname=aryrname,aryrlen=aryrlen,aryrval=aryrval, &
563  aryr8name=aryr8name,aryr8len=aryr8len,aryr8val=aryr8val, &
564  arylname=arylname,aryllen=aryllen,arylval=arylval, &
565  arycname=arycname,aryclen=aryclen,arycval=arycval )
566  if ( ios.ne.0) then
567  if ( present(iret)) then
568  iret=ios
569  return
570  else
571  call nemsio_stop
572  endif
573  endif
574 !------------------------------------------------------------
575 ! if gaction is wrong
576 !------------------------------------------------------------
577  else
578  if ( present(iret)) then
579  return
580  else
581  call nemsio_stop
582  endif
583  endif
584 !------------------------------------------------------------
585 ! set default header
586 !------------------------------------------------------------
587  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headvariname).or. &
588  .not.allocated(gfile%headvarrname).or. &
589  .not.allocated(gfile%headvarcname).or. &
590  .not.allocated(gfile%headvarlname).or. &
591  .not.allocated(gfile%headaryiname).or. &
592  .not.allocated(gfile%headaryrname) ) then
593 
594  call nemsio_setfhead(gfile,ios)
595  if ( present(iret)) iret=ios
596  if ( ios.ne.0) then
597  if (present(iret)) return
598  call nemsio_stop
599  endif
600  endif
601 
602  iret=0
603  end subroutine nemsio_open
604 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
605  subroutine nemsio_close(gfile,iret)
606 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
607 ! abstract: close gfile including closing the file, returning unit number,
608 ! setting file meta data empty
609 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
610  implicit none
611  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
612  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
613  integer(nemsio_intkind) :: ios
614 !------------------------------------------------------------
615 ! close the file
616 !------------------------------------------------------------
617  if ( present(iret) ) iret=-1
618  call baclose(gfile%flunit,ios)
619  if ( ios.ne.0) then
620  if ( present(iret)) then
621  return
622  else
623  call nemsio_stop
624  endif
625  endif
626 !------------------------------------------------------------
627 ! free the file unit
628 !------------------------------------------------------------
629  call nemsio_clslu(gfile,ios)
630  if ( ios.ne.0) then
631  if ( present(iret)) then
632  iret=ios
633  return
634  else
635  call nemsio_stop
636  endif
637  endif
638 !------------------------------------------------------------
639 ! empty gfile meta data
640 !------------------------------------------------------------
641  call nemsio_axmeta(gfile,ios)
642  if ( ios.ne.0) then
643  if ( present(iret)) then
644  iret=ios
645  return
646  else
647  call nemsio_stop
648  endif
649  endif
650  if ( present(iret)) iret=0
651 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
652  end subroutine nemsio_close
653 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
654  subroutine nemsio_rcreate(gfile,gfname,gaction,iret)
655 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
656 ! abstract: read nemsio meta data
657 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
658  implicit none
659  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
660  character*(*),intent(in) :: gfname
661  character*(*),intent(in) :: gaction
662  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
663 !local variables
664  integer(nemsio_intkind) :: ios,nmeta
665  integer(nemsio_intkind8) :: iskip,iread,nread
666  type(nemsio_meta1) :: meta1
667  type(nemsio_meta2) :: meta2
668  type(nemsio_meta3) :: meta3
669  integer(nemsio_intkind) :: i
670  character(nemsio_charkind8),allocatable :: char8var(:)
671  logical(nemsio_logickind) :: lreadcrt,ltlendian
672 !------------------------------------------------------------
673 ! read first meta data record
674 !------------------------------------------------------------
675  iret=-3
676  gfile%do_byteswap=.false.
677  iskip=0
678  iread=nemsio_lmeta1
679  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,meta1)
680  lreadcrt=meta1%lmeta==120.and.(meta1%nmeta<13.and.meta1%nmeta>0).and. &
681  (meta1%version<300000.and.meta1%version>=nemsio_intfill)
682  if(nread.lt.iread) then
683 ! control words not right, file is little endian
684  call nemsio_close(gfile,iret=iret)
685  gfile%file_endian='little_endian'
686  gfile%do_byteswap=.false.
687 !reset unit
688  ltlendian=.true.
689  call nemsio_getlu(gfile,gfname,gaction,iret,ltlendian=ltlendian)
690  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'read') )then
691  call baopenr(gfile%flunit,gfname,ios)
692  if(ios/=0) print *,'Cant open file ',trim(gfname),' ios=',ios
693  else if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gaction),'rdwr') )then
694  call baopen(gfile%flunit,gfname,ios)
695  if(ios/=0) print *,'Cant open file ',trim(gfname),' ios=',ios
696  endif
697  gfile%gfname=gfname
698  gfile%gaction=gaction
699  if(trim(machine_endian)=='big_endian') gfile%do_byteswap=.true.
700  if(trim(machine_endian)=='little_endian') gfile%do_byteswap=.false.
701  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,meta1)
702  if(nread<iread) then
703  print *,'WARNING: the file probably is in mixed endian, the program will STOP!'
704  call nemsio_stop()
705  endif
706 !
707  elseif(.not.lreadcrt) then
708 ! set byteswap
709  gfile%do_byteswap=.true.
710  endif
711 ! --------------------------------------------------------------------
712 !---check endian
713 ! --------------------------------------------------------------------
714  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
715  if(trim(machine_endian)=='big_endian')gfile%file_endian='little_endian'
716  if(trim(machine_endian)=='little_endian')gfile%file_endian='big_endian'
717  else
718  gfile%file_endian=machine_endian
719  endif
720 !
721  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(meta1%version,nemsio_intkind,6)
722 ! --------------------------------------------------------------------
723  gfile%tlmeta=nread
724  gfile%gtype=meta1%gtype
725  gfile%version=meta1%version
726  gfile%nmeta=meta1%nmeta
727  gfile%lmeta=meta1%lmeta
728  gfile%gdatatype=meta1%gdatatype
729  gfile%modelname=meta1%modelname
730 ! print *,'in rcreate,do_byteswap=',gfile%do_byteswap,'machine_endian=', &
731 ! machine_endian,'file_endian=',gfile%file_endian,'gtype=',gfile%gtype, &
732 ! 'version=',gfile%version,gfile%nmeta,gfile%lmeta,gfile%gdatatype,gfile%modelname, &
733 ! 'reserve=',meta1%reserve
734  if ( trim(gfile%gdatatype(1:3)).ne."bin".and.trim(gfile%gdatatype(1:4)).ne."grib" ) then
735  gfile%gdatatype="grib"
736  endif
737  if ( gfile%gtype(1:6) .ne. 'NEMSIO' ) then
738  iret=-9
739  return
740  endif
741 !------------------------------------------------------------
742 ! read second meta data record
743 !------------------------------------------------------------
744  iskip=iskip+nread
745  iread=gfile%lmeta
746  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,meta2)
747 ! print *,'in rcreate,meta2 iskip=',iskip,'iread=',iread,'nread=',nread
748  if(nread.lt.iread) return
749  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
750  call byteswap(meta2%nrec,nemsio_intkind,25)
751  call byteswap(meta2%rlon_min,nemsio_realkind,4)
752  call byteswap(meta2%extrameta,nemsio_logickind,1)
753  endif
754  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
755 ! print *,'tlmeta2 =',gfile%tlmeta,'iskip=',iskip,'iread=',iread,'nread=',nread
756  gfile%nrec=meta2%nrec
757  gfile%idate(1:7)=meta2%idate(1:7)
758  gfile%nfday=meta2%nfday
759  gfile%nfhour=meta2%nfhour
760  gfile%nfminute=meta2%nfminute
761  gfile%nfsecondn=meta2%nfsecondn
762  gfile%nfsecondd=meta2%nfsecondd
763  gfile%dimx=meta2%dimx
764  gfile%dimy=meta2%dimy
765  gfile%dimz=meta2%dimz
766  gfile%nframe=meta2%nframe
767  gfile%nsoil=meta2%nsoil
768  gfile%ntrac=meta2%ntrac
769  gfile%jcap=meta2%jcap
770  gfile%ncldt=meta2%ncldt
771  gfile%idvc=meta2%idvc
772  gfile%idsl=meta2%idsl
773  gfile%idvm=meta2%idvm
774  gfile%idrt=meta2%idrt
775  gfile%rlon_min=meta2%rlon_min
776  gfile%rlon_max=meta2%rlon_max
777  gfile%rlat_min=meta2%rlat_min
778  gfile%rlat_max=meta2%rlat_max
779  gfile%extrameta=meta2%extrameta
780  gfile%fieldsize=(gfile%dimx+2*gfile%nframe)*(gfile%dimy+2*gfile%nframe)
781 
782  nmeta=gfile%nmeta-2
783 !------------------------------------------------------------
784 ! set up gfile required meata arrays
785 !------------------------------------------------------------
786  call nemsio_almeta(gfile,ios)
787  if ( ios .ne. 0 ) then
788  iret=ios
789  return
790  endif
791 !------------------------------------------------------------
792 ! read gfile meta data array (meta rec 3:13)
793 !------------------------------------------------------------
794 !meta3:recname
795  if(gfile%nmeta-2>0) then
796  iskip=iskip+nread
797  iread=len(gfile%recname)*size(gfile%recname)
798  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%recname)
799  if(nread.lt.iread) then
800  iread=nemsio_charkind8*size(gfile%recname)
801  allocate(char8var(size(gfile%recname)))
802  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
803  gfile%recname=char8var
804  deallocate(char8var)
805  if (nread.lt.iread) return
806  endif
807  nmeta=nmeta-1
808  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
809  endif
810 
811  if (gfile%nmeta-3>0 ) then
812 !meta4:reclevtyp
813  iskip=iskip+nread
814  iread=len(gfile%reclevtyp)*size(gfile%reclevtyp)
815  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%reclevtyp)
816  if(nread.lt.iread) return
817  nmeta=nmeta-1
818  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
819  endif
820 
821  if (gfile%nmeta-4 >0 ) then
822 !meta5:reclev
823  iskip=iskip+nread
824  iread=kind(gfile%reclev)*size(gfile%reclev)
825  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%reclev)
826  if(nread.lt.iread) return
827  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%reclev,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%reclev))
828  nmeta=nmeta-1
829  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
830  endif
831 
832  if (gfile%nmeta-5 >0 ) then
833 !meta6:vcoord
834  iskip=iskip+nread
835  iread=kind(gfile%vcoord)*size(gfile%vcoord)
836  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%vcoord)
837  if(nread.lt.iread) return
838  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%vcoord,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%vcoord))
839  nmeta=nmeta-1
840  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
841  endif
842 
843  if ( gfile%nmeta-6>0 ) then
844 !meta7:lat
845  iskip=iskip+nread
846  iread=kind(gfile%lat)*size(gfile%lat)
847  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%lat)
848  if(nread.lt.iread) return
849  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lat,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lat))
850  nmeta=nmeta-1
851  gfile%tlmetalat=gfile%tlmeta
852  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
853  endif
854 
855  if ( gfile%nmeta-7>0 ) then
856 !meta8:lon
857  iskip=iskip+nread
858  iread=kind(gfile%lon)*size(gfile%lon)
859  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%lon)
860  if(nread.lt.iread) return
861  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lon,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lon))
862  nmeta=nmeta-1
863  gfile%tlmetalon=gfile%tlmeta
864  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
865  endif
866 
867  if ( gfile%nmeta-8>0 ) then
868 !meta9:dx
869  iskip=iskip+nread
870  iread=kind(gfile%dx)*size(gfile%dx)
871  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%dx)
872  if(nread.lt.iread) return
873  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dx,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dx))
874  nmeta=nmeta-1
875  gfile%tlmetadx=gfile%tlmeta
876  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
877  endif
878 
879  if ( gfile%nmeta-9>0 ) then
880 !meta10:dy
881  iskip=iskip+nread
882  iread=kind(gfile%dy)*size(gfile%dy)
883  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%dy)
884  if(nread.lt.iread) return
885  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dy,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dy))
886  nmeta=nmeta-1
887  gfile%tlmetady=gfile%tlmeta
888  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
889  endif
890 
891  if ( gfile%nmeta-10>0 ) then
892 !meta11:cpi
893  iskip=iskip+nread
894  iread=kind(gfile%cpi)*size(gfile%Cpi)
895  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%Cpi)
896  if(nread.lt.iread) return
897  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Cpi,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Cpi))
898  nmeta=nmeta-1
899  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
900  endif
901 
902  if ( gfile%nmeta-11>0 ) then
903 !Ri
904  iskip=iskip+nread
905  iread=kind(gfile%ri)*size(gfile%Ri)
906  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%Ri)
907  if(nread.lt.iread) return
908  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Ri,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Ri))
909  nmeta=nmeta-1
910  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
911 ! print *,'tlmetri =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread,'ri=',gfile%ri
912  endif
913 !
914 ! if ( gfile%nmeta-12>0 ) then
915 ! print *,'nmeta=',nmeta,' WARNING:there are more meta to be read!'
916 ! endif
917 
918  if(gfile%extrameta) then
919 !------------------------------------------------------------
920 ! read out extra meta data
921 !------------------------------------------------------------
922  iskip=iskip+nread
923  iread=nemsio_lmeta3
924  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,meta3)
925  if(nread.lt.iread) then
926 !when no r8 var and ary
927  iread=nemsio_lmeta3-8
928  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,meta3)
929  if(nread.lt.iread) return
930  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(meta3%nmetavari,nemsio_intkind,8)
931  else
932  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(meta3%nmetavari,nemsio_intkind,10)
933  gfile%nmetavarr8=meta3%nmetavarr8
934  gfile%nmetaaryr8=meta3%nmetaaryr8
935  endif
936  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
937 ! print *,'after meta3,iskip=',iskip,'iread=',iread,'nread=',nread,'tlmeta=',gfile%tlmeta
938  gfile%nmetavari=meta3%nmetavari
939  gfile%nmetavarr=meta3%nmetavarr
940  gfile%nmetavarl=meta3%nmetavarl
941  gfile%nmetavarc=meta3%nmetavarc
942  gfile%nmetaaryi=meta3%nmetaaryi
943  gfile%nmetaaryr=meta3%nmetaaryr
944  gfile%nmetaaryl=meta3%nmetaaryl
945  gfile%nmetaaryc=meta3%nmetaaryc
946 
947 ! print *,'before nemsio_alextramet,nvar=',gfile%nmetavari,gfile%nmetavarr,gfile%nmetavarl,&
948 ! gfile%nmetavarc,'nary=',gfile%nmetaaryi,gfile%nmetaaryr,gfile%nmetaaryl, &
949 ! gfile%nmetaaryc,'r8ivar ary=',gfile%nmetavarr8,gfile%nmetaaryr8
950  call nemsio_alextrameta(gfile,ios)
951  if ( ios .ne. 0 ) then
952  iret=ios
953  return
954  endif
955 
956 !meta var integer
957  if (gfile%nmetavari.gt.0) then
958  iskip=iskip+nread
959  iread=len(gfile%variname)*gfile%nmetavari
960  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%variname)
961 ! print *,'after get varint name,iskip=',iskip,'iread=',iread,'nread=',nread
962  if(nread.lt.iread) then
963  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetavari
964  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetavari))
965  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
966  gfile%variname=char8var
967  deallocate(char8var)
968 ! print *,'after get varint name8,iskip=',iskip,'iread=',iread,'nread=',nread
969  if (nread.lt.iread) return
970  endif
971  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
972 ! print *,'tlmetavari =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread,'iread=',iread,gfile%nmetavari
973  iskip=iskip+nread
974  iread=nemsio_intkind*gfile%nmetavari
975  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varival)
976  if(nread.lt.iread) return
977  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varival,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%varival))
978  gfile%tlmetavarival=gfile%tlmeta
979  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
980 ! print *,'tlmetavarival =',gfile%tlmetavarival,gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread
981  endif
982 !meta var real
983  if (gfile%nmetavarr.gt.0) then
984  iskip=iskip+nread
985  iread=len(gfile%varrname)*gfile%nmetavarr
986  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varrname)
987 ! print *,'tlmetavarr =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread,'iread=',iread,gfile%nmetavarr
988  if(nread.lt.iread) then
989  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetavarr
990  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetavarr))
991  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
992  gfile%varrname=char8var
993  deallocate(char8var)
994  if (nread.lt.iread) return
995  endif
996  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
997 ! print *,'tlmetavarr =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread,gfile%nmetavarr
998  iskip=iskip+nread
999  iread=kind(gfile%varrval)*gfile%nmetavarr
1000  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varrval)
1001  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1002  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varrval,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%varrval))
1003  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1004 ! print *,'tlmetavarrval =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread
1005  endif
1006 !meta var logical
1007  if (gfile%nmetavarl.gt.0) then
1008  iskip=iskip+nread
1009  iread=len(gfile%varlname)*gfile%nmetavarl
1010  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varlname)
1011  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1012  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetavarl
1013  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetavarl))
1014  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1015  gfile%varlname=char8var
1016  deallocate(char8var)
1017  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1018  endif
1019  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1020 ! print *,'tlmetavarl =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread,gfile%nmetavarl
1021  iskip=iskip+nread
1022  iread=nemsio_logickind*gfile%nmetavarl
1023  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varlval)
1024  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1025  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varlval,nemsio_logickind,size(gfile%varlval))
1026  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1027  endif
1028 !meta var string
1029  if (gfile%nmetavarc.gt.0) then
1030  iskip=iskip+nread
1031  iread=len(gfile%varcname)*gfile%nmetavarc
1032  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varcname)
1033  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1034  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetavarc
1035  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetavarc))
1036  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1037  gfile%varcname=char8var
1038  deallocate(char8var)
1039  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1040  endif
1041  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1042  iskip=iskip+nread
1043  iread=len(gfile%varcval)*gfile%nmetavarc
1044  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varcval)
1045  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1046  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1047  endif
1048 !meta var real 8
1049  if (gfile%nmetavarr8.gt.0) then
1050  iskip=iskip+nread
1051  iread=len(gfile%varr8name)*gfile%nmetavarr8
1052  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varr8name)
1053  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1054  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetavarr8
1055  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetavarr8))
1056  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1057  gfile%varr8name=char8var
1058  deallocate(char8var)
1059  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1060  endif
1061  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1062  iskip=iskip+nread
1063  iread=kind(gfile%varr8val)*gfile%nmetavarr8
1064  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%varr8val)
1065  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1066  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varr8val,nemsio_dblekind,size(gfile%varr8val))
1067  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1068  endif
1069 !
1070 !meta arr integeryy
1071  if (gfile%nmetaaryi.gt.0) then
1072  iskip=iskip+nread
1073  iread=len(gfile%aryiname)*gfile%nmetaaryi
1074  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryiname)
1075  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1076  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetaaryi
1077  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetaaryi))
1078  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1079  gfile%aryiname=char8var
1080  deallocate(char8var)
1081  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1082  endif
1083  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1084 ! print *,'tlmetaaryinam =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread
1085  iskip=iskip+nread
1086  iread=kind(gfile%nmetaaryi)*gfile%nmetaaryi
1087  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryilen)
1088  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1089  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryilen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryilen))
1090  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1091  gfile%tlmetaaryival=gfile%tlmeta
1092 ! print *,'tlmetaaryilen =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread
1093  allocate(gfile%aryival(maxval(gfile%aryilen),gfile%nmetaaryi))
1094  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryi
1095  iskip=iskip+nread
1096  iread=kind(gfile%aryival)*gfile%aryilen(i)
1097  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryival(:,i))
1098  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1099  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryival(:,i),nemsio_intkind,gfile%aryilen(i))
1100  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1101 
1102 ! print *,'tlmetaaryival =',gfile%tlmeta,'nread=',nread
1103  enddo
1104  endif
1105 !meta arr real4
1106  if (gfile%nmetaaryr.gt.0) then
1107  iskip=iskip+nread
1108  iread=len(gfile%aryrname)*gfile%nmetaaryr
1109  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryrname)
1110  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1111  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetaaryr
1112  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetaaryr))
1113  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1114  gfile%aryrname=char8var
1115  deallocate(char8var)
1116  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1117  endif
1118  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1119  iskip=iskip+nread
1120  iread=kind(gfile%aryrlen)*gfile%nmetaaryr
1121  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryrlen)
1122  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1123  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrlen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryrlen))
1124  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1125  allocate(gfile%aryrval(maxval(gfile%aryrlen),gfile%nmetaaryr) )
1126  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryr
1127  iskip=iskip+nread
1128  iread=kind(gfile%aryrval)*gfile%aryrlen(i)
1129  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryrval(:,i))
1130  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1131  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrval(:,i),nemsio_realkind,gfile%aryrlen(i))
1132  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1133  enddo
1134  endif
1135 !meta arr logical
1136  if (gfile%nmetaaryl.gt.0) then
1137  iskip=iskip+nread
1138  iread=len(gfile%arylname)*gfile%nmetaaryl
1139  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%arylname)
1140  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1141  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetaaryl
1142  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetaaryl))
1143  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1144  gfile%arylname=char8var
1145  deallocate(char8var)
1146  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1147  endif
1148  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1149  iskip=iskip+nread
1150  iread=kind(gfile%aryllen)*gfile%nmetaaryl
1151  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryllen)
1152  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1153  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryllen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryllen))
1154  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1155  allocate(gfile%arylval(maxval(gfile%aryllen),gfile%nmetaaryl) )
1156  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryl
1157  iskip=iskip+nread
1158  iread=kind(gfile%arylval)*gfile%aryllen(i)
1159  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%arylval(:,i))
1160  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1161  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%arylval(:,i),nemsio_logickind,gfile%aryllen(i))
1162  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1163  enddo
1164  endif
1165 !meta arr char
1166  if (gfile%nmetaaryc.gt.0) then
1167  iskip=iskip+nread
1168  iread=len(gfile%arycname)*gfile%nmetaaryc
1169  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%arycname)
1170  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1171  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetaaryc
1172  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetaaryc))
1173  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1174  gfile%arycname=char8var
1175  deallocate(char8var)
1176  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1177  endif
1178  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1179  iskip=iskip+nread
1180  iread=kind(gfile%aryclen)*gfile%nmetaaryc
1181  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryclen)
1182  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1183  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryclen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryclen))
1184  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1185  allocate(gfile%arycval(maxval(gfile%aryclen),gfile%nmetaaryc) )
1186  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryc
1187  iskip=iskip+nread
1188  iread=len(gfile%arycval)*gfile%aryclen(i)
1189  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%arycval(:,i))
1190  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1191  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1192  enddo
1193  endif
1194 !meta arr real8
1195  if (gfile%nmetaaryr8.gt.0) then
1196  iskip=iskip+nread
1197  iread=len(gfile%aryr8name)*gfile%nmetaaryr8
1198  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryr8name)
1199  if(nread.lt.iread) then
1200  iread=nemsio_charkind8*gfile%nmetaaryr8
1201  allocate(char8var(gfile%nmetaaryr8))
1202  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,char8var)
1203  gfile%aryr8name=char8var
1204  deallocate(char8var)
1205  if (nread.lt.iread) return
1206  endif
1207  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1208  iskip=iskip+nread
1209  iread=kind(gfile%aryr8len)*gfile%nmetaaryr8
1210  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryr8len)
1211  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1212  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8len,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryr8len))
1213  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1214  allocate(gfile%aryr8val(maxval(gfile%aryr8len),gfile%nmetaaryr8) )
1215  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryr8
1216  iskip=iskip+nread
1217  iread=kind(gfile%aryr8val)*gfile%aryr8len(i)
1218  call bafrreadl(gfile%flunit,iskip,iread,nread,gfile%aryr8val(:,i))
1219  if(nread.lt.iread) return
1220  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8val(:,i),nemsio_dblekind,gfile%aryr8len(i))
1221  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nread
1222  enddo
1223  endif
1224 !
1225 !end if extrameta
1226  endif
1227 !
1228 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
1229  iret=0
1230  end subroutine nemsio_rcreate
1231 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1232  subroutine nemsio_wcreate(gfile,gfname,gaction,iret,gdatatype,version, &
1233  nmeta,lmeta,modelname,nrec,idate,nfday, &
1234  nfhour,nfminute,nfsecondn,nfsecondd, &
1235  dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe,nsoil,ntrac,jcap,ncldt,idvc,idsl,idvm,idrt, &
1236  rlon_min,rlon_max,rlat_min,rlat_max,extrameta, &
1237  nmetavari,nmetavarr,nmetavarl,nmetavarc,nmetavarr8, &
1238  nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl,nmetaaryc,nmetaaryr8, &
1239  recname,reclevtyp,reclev,vcoord,lat,lon,dx,dy,cpi,ri, &
1240  variname,varival,varrname,varrval,varlname,varlval,varcname,varcval, &
1241  varr8name,varr8val, &
1242  aryiname,aryilen,aryival,aryrname,aryrlen,aryrval, &
1243  arylname,aryllen,arylval,arycname,aryclen,arycval, &
1244  aryr8name,aryr8len,aryr8val )
1245 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
1246 ! abstract: write nemsio meta data
1247 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
1248  implicit none
1249  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
1250  character*(*),intent(in) :: gfname
1251  character*(*),intent(in) :: gaction
1252  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
1253 !optional variables
1254  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: gdatatype,modelname
1255  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: version,nmeta,lmeta,nrec
1256  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: idate(7),nfday,nfhour, &
1257  nfminute,nfsecondn,nfsecondd
1258  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe, &
1259  nsoil,ntrac
1260  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: jcap,ncldt,idvc,idsl, &
1261  idvm,idrt
1262  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: rlat_min,rlat_max, &
1263  rlon_min,rlon_max
1264  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(in):: extrameta
1265  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: nmetavari,nmetavarr, &
1266  nmetavarl,nmetavarc,nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl,nmetaaryc, &
1267  nmetavarr8,nmetaaryr8
1268 !
1269  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: recname(:),reclevtyp(:)
1270  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: reclev(:)
1271  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: vcoord(:,:,:)
1272  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: lat(:),lon(:)
1273  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: dx(:),dy(:)
1274  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: Cpi(:),Ri(:)
1275 !
1276  character*(*),optional,intent(in) :: variname(:),varrname(:),&
1277  varlname(:),varcname(:),varr8name(:),aryiname(:),aryrname(:), &
1278  arylname(:),arycname(:),aryr8name(:)
1279  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: aryilen(:),aryrlen(:), &
1280  aryllen(:),aryclen(:),aryr8len(:)
1281  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: varival(:),aryival(:,:)
1282  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: varrval(:),aryrval(:,:)
1283  real(nemsio_dblekind),optional,intent(in) :: varr8val(:),aryr8val(:,:)
1284  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(in):: varlval(:),arylval(:,:)
1285  character(*),optional,intent(in) :: varcval(:),arycval(:,:)
1286 !
1287 !--- local variables
1288 !
1289  real(nemsio_realkind) :: radi
1290  integer(nemsio_intkind8) :: iskip,iwrite,nwrite
1291  type(nemsio_meta1) :: meta1
1292  type(nemsio_meta2) :: meta2
1293  type(nemsio_meta3) :: meta3
1294  integer(nemsio_intkind) :: i,n,ios,nummeta
1295  logical :: linit,ltlendian
1296  character(nemsio_charkind8) :: tmpgdatatype
1297 !------------------------------------------------------------
1298 ! set gfile meta data to operational model (default) if it's empty
1299 !------------------------------------------------------------
1300  iret=-3
1301 !first decide file endian
1302  gfile%file_endian='big_endian'
1303  if(present(gdatatype)) then
1304  if ( trim(gdatatype(1:4)).ne.'grib'.and.gdatatype(1:3).ne.'bin'.and. &
1305  trim(gdatatype).ne.'') return
1306  gfile%gdatatype=gdatatype
1307  if(trim(gfile%gdatatype(6:7))=='be')then
1308  gfile%file_endian='big_endian'
1309  elseif(trim(gfile%gdatatype(6:7))=='le') then
1310  gfile%file_endian='little_endian'
1311  endif
1312  elseif(trim(gfile%gdatatype).eq.'') then
1313  gfile%gdatatype='grib'
1314  endif
1315  tmpgdatatype=gfile%gdatatype
1316 !
1317  if(gfile%file_endian=='little_endian') then
1318 ! file is little endian
1319  call nemsio_close(gfile,iret=iret)
1320 ! reset file unit
1321  gfile%file_endian='little_endian'
1322  gfile%gdatatype=tmpgdatatype
1323  gfile%gfname=gfname
1324  gfile%gaction=gaction

1776  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1777  iwrite=kind(gfile%lat)*size(gfile%lat)
1778  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lat,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lat))
1779  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%lat)
1780  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1781  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lat,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lat))
1782  gfile%tlmetalat=gfile%tlmeta
1783  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1784  nummeta=nummeta-1
1785  endif
1786 !lon
1787  if ( nummeta.gt.0 ) then
1788  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1789  iwrite=kind(gfile%lon)*size(gfile%lon)
1790  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lon,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lon))
1791  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%lon)
1792  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1793  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lon,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lon))
1794  gfile%tlmetalon=gfile%tlmeta
1795  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1796  nummeta=nummeta-1
1797  endif
1798 !dx
1799  if ( nummeta.gt.0 ) then
1800  if(all(gfile%dx==0.)) gfile%dx=nemsio_realfill
1801  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1802  iwrite=kind(gfile%dx)*size(gfile%dx)
1803  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dx,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dx))
1804  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%dx)
1805  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dx,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dx))
1806  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1807  gfile%tlmetadx=gfile%tlmeta
1808  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1809  nummeta=nummeta-1
1810  endif
1811 !dy
1812  if ( nummeta.gt.0 ) then
1813  if(all(gfile%dy==0.)) gfile%dy=nemsio_realfill
1814  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1815  iwrite=kind(gfile%dy)*size(gfile%dy)
1816  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dy,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dy))
1817  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%dy)
1818  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1819  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dy,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dy))
1820  gfile%tlmetady=gfile%tlmeta
1821  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1822  nummeta=nummeta-1
1823  endif
1824 !Cpi
1825  if ( nummeta.gt.0 ) then
1826  if(all(gfile%cpi==0.)) gfile%cpi=nemsio_realfill
1827  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1828  iwrite=kind(gfile%Cpi)*size(gfile%Cpi)
1829  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Cpi,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Cpi))
1830  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%Cpi)
1831  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1832  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Cpi,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Cpi))
1833  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1834  nummeta=nummeta-1
1835  endif
1836 !Ri
1837  if ( nummeta.gt.0 ) then
1838  if(all(gfile%ri==0.)) gfile%ri=nemsio_realfill
1839  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1840  iwrite=kind(gfile%Ri)*size(gfile%Ri)
1841  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Ri,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Ri))
1842  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%Ri)
1843  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1844  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%Ri,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%Ri))
1845  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1846  nummeta=nummeta-1
1847  endif
1848 !------------------------------------------------------------
1849 ! write out extra meta data record
1850 !------------------------------------------------------------
1851  if(gfile%extrameta) then
1852  meta3%nmetavari=gfile%nmetavari
1853  meta3%nmetavarr=gfile%nmetavarr
1854  meta3%nmetavarl=gfile%nmetavarl
1855  meta3%nmetavarc=gfile%nmetavarc
1856  meta3%nmetaaryi=gfile%nmetaaryi
1857  meta3%nmetaaryr=gfile%nmetaaryr
1858  meta3%nmetaaryl=gfile%nmetaaryl
1859  meta3%nmetaaryc=gfile%nmetaaryc
1860  meta3%nmetavarr8=gfile%nmetavarr8
1861  meta3%nmetaaryr8=gfile%nmetaaryr8
1862  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1863  if(gfile%nmetavarr8>0.or.gfile%nmetaaryr8>0) then
1864  iwrite=nemsio_lmeta3
1865  else
1866  iwrite=nemsio_lmeta3-8
1867  endif
1868  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(meta3%nmetavari,nemsio_intkind,10)
1869  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,meta3)
1870  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(meta3%nmetavari,nemsio_intkind,10)
1871  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1872  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1873 !
1874 !-- write meta var integer
1875  if (gfile%nmetavari.gt.0) then
1876  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1877  iwrite=len(gfile%variname)*gfile%nmetavari
1878  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%variname)
1879 ! print *,'tlmetavari=',gfile%tlmeta,'iwrite=',iwrite,'nwrite=',nwrite
1880  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1881  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1882  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1883  iwrite=kind(gfile%varival)*gfile%nmetavari
1884  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varival,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%varival))
1885  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varival)
1886 ! print *,'tlmetavarival=',gfile%tlmeta,'iwrite=',iwrite,'nwrite=',nwrite
1887  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1888  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varival,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%varival))
1889  gfile%tlmetavarival=gfile%tlmeta
1890  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1891  endif
1892 !var real4
1893  if (gfile%nmetavarr.gt.0) then
1894  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1895  iwrite=len(gfile%varrname)*gfile%nmetavarr
1896  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varrname)
1897 ! print *,'tlmetavarr=',gfile%tlmeta,'iwrite=',iwrite,'nwrite=',nwrite
1898  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1899  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1900  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1901  iwrite=kind(gfile%varrval)*gfile%nmetavarr
1902  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varrval,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%varrval))
1903  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varrval)
1904  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1905  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varrval,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%varrval))
1906  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1907  endif
1908 !var logical
1909  if (gfile%nmetavarl.gt.0) then
1910  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1911  iwrite=len(gfile%varlname)*gfile%nmetavarl
1912  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varlname)
1913  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1914  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite

1917  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varlval,nemsio_logickind,size(gfile%varlval))
1918  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varlval)
1919  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1920  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varlval,nemsio_logickind,size(gfile%varlval))
1921  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1922  endif

1924  if (gfile%nmetavarc.gt.0) then
1925  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1926  iwrite=len(gfile%varcname)*gfile%nmetavarc
1927  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varcname)

1931  iwrite=len(gfile%varcval)*gfile%nmetavarc
1932  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varcval)
1933  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1934  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1935  endif
1936 !var real8
1937  if (gfile%nmetavarr8.gt.0) then
1938  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1939  iwrite=len(gfile%varr8name)*gfile%nmetavarr8
1940  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varr8name)
1941  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1942  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1943  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1944  iwrite=kind(gfile%varr8val)*gfile%nmetavarr8
1945  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varr8val,nemsio_dblekind,size(gfile%varr8val))
1946  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varr8val)
1947  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1948  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varr8val,nemsio_dblekind,size(gfile%varr8val))
1949  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1950  endif
1951 !meta arr integer
1952  if (gfile%nmetaaryi.gt.0) then
1953  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1954  iwrite=len(gfile%aryiname)*gfile%nmetaaryi
1955  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryiname)
1956  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1957  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1958  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1959  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryilen)*gfile%nmetaaryi
1960  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryilen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryilen))
1961  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryilen)
1962  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1963  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryilen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryilen))
1964  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1965  gfile%tlmetaaryival=gfile%tlmeta
1966  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryi
1967  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1968  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryival)*gfile%aryilen(i)
1969  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryival(:,i),nemsio_intkind,gfile%aryilen(i))
1970  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
1971  gfile%aryival(1:gfile%aryilen(i),i))
1972  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryival(:,i),nemsio_intkind,gfile%aryilen(i))
1973  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1974  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1975  enddo
1976  endif
1977 !meta arr real
1978  if (gfile%nmetaaryr.gt.0) then
1979  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1980  iwrite=len(gfile%aryrname)*gfile%nmetaaryr
1981  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryrname)
1982  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1983  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1984  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1985  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryrlen)*gfile%nmetaaryr
1986  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrlen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryrlen))
1987  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryrlen)
1988  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1989  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrlen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryrlen))
1990  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
1991  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryr
1992  iskip=iskip+nwrite
1993  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryrval)*gfile%aryrlen(i)
1994  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrval(:,i),nemsio_realkind,gfile%aryrlen(i))
1995  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
1996  gfile%aryrval(1:gfile%aryrlen(i),i))
1997  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryrval(:,i),nemsio_realkind,gfile%aryrlen(i))
1998  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
1999  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2000  enddo
2001  endif
2002 !meta arr logical
2003  if (gfile%nmetaaryl.gt.0) then
2004  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2005  iwrite=len(gfile%arylname)*gfile%nmetaaryl
2006  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%arylname)
2007  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2008  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2009  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2010  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryllen)*gfile%nmetaaryl
2011  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryllen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryllen))
2012  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryllen)
2013  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2014  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryllen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryllen))
2015  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2016  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryl
2017  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2018  iwrite=kind(gfile%arylval)*gfile%aryllen(i)
2019  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%arylval(:,i),nemsio_logickind,gfile%aryllen(i))
2020  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
2021  gfile%arylval(1:gfile%aryllen(i),i))
2022  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2023  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%arylval(:,i),nemsio_logickind,gfile%aryllen(i))
2024  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2025  enddo
2026  endif
2027 !meta arr character array
2028  if (gfile%nmetaaryc.gt.0) then
2029  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2030  iwrite=len(gfile%arycname)*gfile%nmetaaryc
2031  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%arycname)
2032  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2033  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2034  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2035  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryclen)*gfile%nmetaaryc
2036  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryclen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryclen))
2037  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryclen)
2038  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2039  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryclen,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryclen))
2040  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2041  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryc
2042  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2043  iwrite=len(gfile%arycval)*gfile%aryclen(i)
2044  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
2045  gfile%arycval(1:gfile%aryclen(i),i))
2046  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2047  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2048  enddo
2049  endif
2050 !meta arr real8
2051  if (gfile%nmetaaryr8.gt.0) then
2052  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2053  iwrite=len(gfile%aryr8name)*gfile%nmetaaryr8
2054  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryr8name)
2055  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2056  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2057  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2058  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryr8len)*gfile%nmetaaryr8
2059  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8len,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryr8len))
2060  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%aryr8len)
2061  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2062  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8len,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%aryr8len))
2063  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2064  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryr8
2065  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2066  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryr8val)*gfile%aryr8len(i)
2067  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8val(:,i),nemsio_dblekind,gfile%aryr8len(i))
2068  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
2069  gfile%aryr8val(1:gfile%aryr8len(i),i))
2070  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2071  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryr8val(:,i),nemsio_dblekind,gfile%aryr8len(i))
2072  gfile%tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta+nwrite
2073  enddo
2074  endif
2075 
2076  endif
2077 
2078  iret=0
2079 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
2080  end subroutine nemsio_wcreate
2081 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2082  subroutine nemsio_setfheadvari(gfile,varname,varval,iret)
2083 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2084 ! abstract: reset meta data integer value from file header, ONLY for time
2085 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2086  implicit none
2087  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
2088  character(len=*), intent(in) :: varname
2089  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(in) :: varval
2090  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
2091  integer i,j,lhead
2092  integer(nemsio_intkind8) :: iskip,iwrite,nwrite
2093  type(nemsio_meta2) :: meta2
2094 !---
2095  if(present(iret) ) iret=-17
2096  lhead=0
2097 !--- only allow change time in second meta data
2098  if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'nfday')) then
2099  gfile%nfday=varval
2100  gfile%headvarival(5)=varval
2101  lhead=1
2102  else if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'nfhour')) then
2103  gfile%nfhour=varval
2104  gfile%headvarival(6)=varval
2105  lhead=1
2106  else if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'nfminute')) then
2107  gfile%nfminute=varval
2108  gfile%headvarival(7)=varval
2109  lhead=1
2110  else if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'nfsecondd')) then
2111  gfile%nfsecondd=varval
2112  gfile%headvarival(8)=varval
2113  lhead=1
2114  else if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'nfsecondn')) then
2115  gfile%nfsecondn=varval
2116  gfile%headvarival(9)=varval
2117  lhead=1
2118  endif
2119  if(lhead==1) then
2120 ! print *,'in setfhearvari,2,nfday=',gfile%nfday,'nfhour=',gfile%nfhour, &
2121 ! 'nfminute=',gfile%nfminute,'secd=',gfile%nfsecondd,'nsecn=',gfile%nfsecondn
2122 !------------------------------------------------------------
2123 ! write out second meta data record
2124 !------------------------------------------------------------
2125  meta2%nrec=gfile%nrec
2126  meta2%idate(1:7)=gfile%idate(1:7)
2127  meta2%nfday=gfile%nfday
2128  meta2%nfhour=gfile%nfhour
2129  meta2%nfminute=gfile%nfminute
2130  meta2%nfsecondn=gfile%nfsecondn
2131  meta2%nfsecondd=gfile%nfsecondd
2132  meta2%dimx=gfile%dimx
2133  meta2%dimy=gfile%dimy
2134  meta2%dimz=gfile%dimz
2135  meta2%nframe=gfile%nframe
2136  meta2%nsoil=gfile%nsoil
2137  meta2%ntrac=gfile%ntrac
2138  meta2%jcap=gfile%jcap
2139  meta2%ncldt=gfile%ncldt
2140  meta2%idvc=gfile%idvc
2141  meta2%idsl=gfile%idsl
2142  meta2%idvm=gfile%idvm
2143  meta2%idrt=gfile%idrt
2144  meta2%rlon_min=gfile%rlon_min
2145  meta2%rlon_max=gfile%rlon_max
2146  meta2%rlat_min=gfile%rlat_min
2147  meta2%rlat_max=gfile%rlat_max
2148  meta2%extrameta=gfile%extrameta
2149  iskip=nemsio_lmeta1+8
2150  iwrite=gfile%lmeta
2151  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
2152  call byteswap(meta2%nrec,nemsio_intkind,25)
2153  call byteswap(meta2%rlon_min,nemsio_realkind,4)
2154  call byteswap(meta2%extrameta,nemsio_logickind,1)
2155  endif
2156  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,meta2)
2157  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2158  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
2159  call byteswap(meta2%nrec,nemsio_intkind,25)
2160  call byteswap(meta2%rlon_min,nemsio_realkind,4)
2161  call byteswap(meta2%extrameta,nemsio_logickind,1)
2162  endif
2163  if(present(iret)) iret=0
2164  return
2165  endif
2166 !---
2167  if(gfile%nmetavari.gt.0) then
2168  do i=1,gfile%nmetavari
2169  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),trim(gfile%variname(i))) ) then
2170  gfile%varival(i)=varval
2171  iskip=gfile%tlmetavarival
2172  iwrite=kind(gfile%varival)*gfile%nmetavari
2173  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varival,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%varival))
2174  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%varival)
2175  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2176  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%varival,nemsio_intkind,size(gfile%varival))
2177  if(present(iret)) iret=0
2178  return
2179  endif
2180  enddo
2181  endif
2182 !---
2183  if(.not.present(iret)) call nemsio_stop
2184  return
2185  end subroutine nemsio_setfheadvari
2186 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2187  subroutine nemsio_setfheadaryi(gfile,varname,varval,iret)
2188 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2189 ! abstract: reset meta data integer value from file header, ONLY for time
2190 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2191  implicit none
2192  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
2193  character(len=*), intent(in) :: varname
2194  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(in) :: varval(:)
2195  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
2196  integer i,j,lhead
2197  integer(nemsio_intkind8) :: iskip,iwrite,nwrite
2198  type(nemsio_meta2) :: meta2
2199 !---
2200  if(present(iret) ) iret=-17
2201 !--- only allow to change time in second meta data
2202  if (equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),'idate')) then
2203  if(size(gfile%idate)==size(varval)) then
2204  gfile%idate(:)=varval(:)
2205  gfile%headaryival(:,1)=varval(:)
2206 !------------------------------------------------------------
2207 ! write out second meta data record
2208 !------------------------------------------------------------
2209  meta2%nrec=gfile%nrec
2210  meta2%idate(1:7)=gfile%idate(1:7)
2211  meta2%nfday=gfile%nfday
2212  meta2%nfhour=gfile%nfhour
2213  meta2%nfminute=gfile%nfminute
2214  meta2%nfsecondn=gfile%nfsecondn
2215  meta2%nfsecondd=gfile%nfsecondd
2216  meta2%dimx=gfile%dimx
2217  meta2%dimy=gfile%dimy
2218  meta2%dimz=gfile%dimz
2219  meta2%nframe=gfile%nframe
2220  meta2%nsoil=gfile%nsoil
2221  meta2%ntrac=gfile%ntrac
2222  meta2%jcap=gfile%jcap
2223  meta2%ncldt=gfile%ncldt
2224  meta2%idvc=gfile%idvc
2225  meta2%idsl=gfile%idsl
2226  meta2%idvm=gfile%idvm
2227  meta2%idrt=gfile%idrt
2228  meta2%rlon_min=gfile%rlon_min
2229  meta2%rlon_max=gfile%rlon_max
2230  meta2%rlat_min=gfile%rlat_min
2231  meta2%rlat_max=gfile%rlat_max
2232  meta2%extrameta=gfile%extrameta
2233  iskip=nemsio_lmeta1+8
2234  iwrite=gfile%lmeta
2235  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
2236  call byteswap(meta2%nrec,nemsio_intkind,25)
2237  call byteswap(meta2%rlon_min,nemsio_realkind,4)
2238  call byteswap(meta2%extrameta,nemsio_logickind,1)
2239  endif
2240  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,meta2)
2241  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2242  if(gfile%do_byteswap) then
2243  call byteswap(meta2%nrec,nemsio_intkind,25)
2244  call byteswap(meta2%rlon_min,nemsio_realkind,4)
2245  call byteswap(meta2%extrameta,nemsio_logickind,1)
2246  endif
2247  if(present(iret)) iret=0
2248  return
2249  endif
2250  endif
2251 !---
2252  if(gfile%nmetaaryi.gt.0) then
2253  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryi
2254  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(varname),trim(gfile%aryiname(i))) ) then
2255  if(gfile%aryilen(i)==size(varval)) then
2256  gfile%aryival(1:gfile%aryilen(i),i)=varval(1:size(varval))
2257  lhead=1
2258  exit
2259  endif
2260  endif
2261  enddo
2262  if(lhead==1) then
2263  iskip=gfile%tlmetaaryival
2264  nwrite=0
2265  do i=1,gfile%nmetaaryi
2266  iskip=iskip+nwrite
2267  iwrite=kind(gfile%aryival)*gfile%aryilen(i)
2268  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryival(:,i),nemsio_intkind,gfile%aryilen(i))
2269  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite, &
2270  gfile%aryival(1:gfile%aryilen(i),i))
2271  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2272  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%aryival(:,i),nemsio_intkind,gfile%aryilen(i))
2273  enddo
2274  if(present(iret)) iret=0
2275  return
2276  endif
2277  endif
2278 !---
2279  if(.not.present(iret)) call nemsio_stop
2280  return
2281  end subroutine nemsio_setfheadaryi
2282 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2283  subroutine nemsio_setfilehead(gfile,iret,lat,lon,dx,dy)
2284 !
2285 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2286 ! abstract: reset some nemsio meta data information from outside
2287 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2288 !
2289  implicit none
2290  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
2291  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
2292  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: lat(:),lon(:)
2293  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: dx(:),dy(:)
2294 !
2295 !--- local vars
2296  integer(nemsio_intkind8) :: iskip,iwrite,nwrite
2297 !
2298 !---
2299  if (present(iret)) iret=-3
2300 !
2301 !--- check the size first, then set the value
2302 !--- lat
2303  if(present(lat) ) then
2304  if (size(lat).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2305  if ( present(iret)) return
2306  call nemsio_stop
2307  else
2308  gfile%lat=lat
2309  gfile%headaryrval(:,2)=gfile%lat
2310  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),'write') .and. &
2311  gfile%tlmetalat/=nemsio_intfill8) then
2312  iskip=gfile%tlmetalat
2313  iwrite=kind(gfile%lat)*size(gfile%lat)
2314  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lat,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lat))
2315  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%lat)
2316  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2317  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lat,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lat))
2318  endif
2319  endif
2320  endif
2321 !--- lon
2322  if(present(lon) ) then
2323  if (size(lon).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2324  if ( present(iret)) return
2325  call nemsio_stop
2326  else
2327  gfile%lon=lon
2328  gfile%headaryrval(:,3)=gfile%lon
2329  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),'write').and. &
2330  gfile%tlmetalon/=nemsio_intfill8) then
2331  iskip=gfile%tlmetalon
2332  iwrite=kind(gfile%lon)*size(gfile%lon)
2333  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lon,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lon))
2334  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%lon)
2335  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2336  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%lon,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%lon))
2337  endif
2338  endif
2339  endif
2340 !--- dx
2341  if(present(dx) ) then
2342  if (size(dx).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2343  if ( present(iret)) return
2344  call nemsio_stop
2345  else
2346  gfile%dx=dx
2347  gfile%headaryrval(:,4)=gfile%dx
2348  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),'write').and. &
2349  gfile%tlmetadx/=nemsio_intfill8) then
2350  iskip=gfile%tlmetadx
2351  iwrite=kind(gfile%dx)*size(gfile%dx)
2352  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dx,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dx))
2353  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%dx)
2354  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2355  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dx,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dx))
2356  endif
2357  endif
2358  endif
2359 !--- dy
2360  if(present(dy) ) then
2361  if (size(dy).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2362  if ( present(iret)) return
2363  call nemsio_stop
2364  else
2365  gfile%dy=dy
2366  gfile%headaryrval(:,5)=gfile%dy
2367  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),'write').and. &
2368  gfile%tlmetady/=nemsio_intfill8) then
2369  iskip=gfile%tlmetady
2370  iwrite=kind(gfile%dy)*size(gfile%dy)
2371  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dy,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dy))
2372  call bafrwritel(gfile%flunit,iskip,iwrite,nwrite,gfile%dy)
2373  if(nwrite.lt.iwrite) return
2374  if(gfile%do_byteswap) call byteswap(gfile%dy,nemsio_realkind,size(gfile%dy))
2375  endif
2376  endif
2377  endif
2378 !
2379  iret=0
2380 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
2381  end subroutine nemsio_setfilehead

2383 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2384  subroutine nemsio_getfilehead(gfile,iret,gtype,gdatatype,gfname,gaction, &
2385  modelname,version,nmeta,lmeta,nrec,idate,nfday,nfhour,nfminute, &
2386  nfsecondn,nfsecondd,dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe,nsoil,ntrac,ncldt,jcap, &
2387  idvc,idsl,idvm,idrt, rlon_min,rlon_max,rlat_min,rlat_max, &
2388  tlmeta,flunit, file_endian,do_byteswap, &
2389  extrameta,nmetavari,nmetavarr,nmetavarl,nmetavarc,nmetavarr8, &
2390  nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl,nmetaaryc,nmetaaryr8, &
2391  recname,reclevtyp,reclev,vcoord,lon,lat,dx,dy,cpi,ri, &
2392  variname,varival,varrname,varrval,varlname,varlval,varcname,varcval, &
