2395  arylname,aryllen,arylval,arycname,aryclen,arycval, &
2396  aryr8name,aryr8len,aryr8val )
2397 
2398 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2399 ! abstract: get nemsio meta data information from outside
2400 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
2401  implicit none
2402  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(in) :: gfile
2403  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
2404  character*(*),optional,intent(out) :: gtype,gdatatype,gfname, &
2405  gaction,modelname
2406  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: version,nmeta,lmeta
2407  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: nrec,idate(7),nfday,nfhour, &
2408  nfminute,nfsecondn,nfsecondd
2409  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: dimx,dimy,dimz,nframe, &
2410  nsoil,ntrac
2411  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: ncldt,jcap,idvc,idsl,idvm,idrt
2412  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: rlon_min,rlon_max,rlat_min, &
2413  rlat_max
2414  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: tlmeta
2415  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: flunit
2416  character*(*),optional,intent(out) :: file_endian
2417  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(out):: do_byteswap
2418  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(out):: extrameta
2419  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: nmetavari,nmetavarr, &
2420  nmetavarl,nmetavarc,nmetavarr8, &
2421  nmetaaryi,nmetaaryr,nmetaaryl, &
2422  nmetaaryc,nmetaaryr8
2423  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: recname(:)
2424  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: reclevtyp(:)
2425  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: reclev(:)
2426  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: vcoord(:,:,:)
2427  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: lat(:),lon(:)
2428  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: dx(:),dy(:)
2429  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: cpi(:),ri(:)
2430  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: variname(:),varrname(:)
2431  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: varlname(:),varcname(:)
2432  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: varr8name(:)
2433  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: aryiname(:),aryrname(:)
2434  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: arylname(:),arycname(:)
2435  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: aryr8name(:)
2436  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: aryilen(:),aryrlen(:)
2437  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: aryllen(:),aryclen(:)
2438  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: aryr8len(:)
2439  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: varival(:),aryival(:,:)
2440  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(out) :: varrval(:),aryrval(:,:)
2441  real(nemsio_dblekind),optional,intent(out) :: varr8val(:),aryr8val(:,:)
2442  logical(nemsio_logickind),optional,intent(out):: varlval(:),arylval(:,:)
2443  character(*),optional,intent(out) :: varcval(:),arycval(:,:)
2444 !
2445  integer i,j
2446 !------------------------------------------------------------
2447  if (present(iret)) iret=-3
2448  if(present(gtype)) gtype=gfile%gtype
2449  if(present(gdatatype)) gdatatype=gfile%gdatatype
2450  if(present(gfname)) gfname=trim(gfile%gfname)
2451  if(present(gaction)) gaction=gfile%gaction
2452  if(present(modelname)) modelname=gfile%modelname
2453  if(present(version)) version=gfile%version
2454  if(present(nmeta)) nmeta=gfile%nmeta
2455  if(present(lmeta)) lmeta=gfile%lmeta
2456  if(present(nrec)) nrec=gfile%nrec
2457  if(present(nfday)) nfday=gfile%nfday
2458  if(present(nfhour)) nfhour=gfile%nfhour
2459  if(present(nfminute)) nfminute=gfile%nfminute
2460  if(present(nfsecondn)) nfsecondn=gfile%nfsecondn
2461  if(present(nfsecondd)) nfsecondd=gfile%nfsecondd
2462  if(present(idate)) idate=gfile%idate
2463  if(present(dimx)) dimx=gfile%dimx
2464  if(present(dimy)) dimy=gfile%dimy
2465  if(present(dimz)) dimz=gfile%dimz
2466  if(present(nframe)) nframe=gfile%nframe
2467  if(present(nsoil)) nsoil=gfile%nsoil
2468  if(present(ntrac)) ntrac=gfile%ntrac
2469  if(present(jcap)) jcap=gfile%jcap
2470  if(present(ncldt)) ncldt=gfile%ncldt
2471  if(present(idvc)) idvc=gfile%idvc
2472  if(present(idsl)) idsl=gfile%idsl
2473  if(present(idvm)) idvm=gfile%idvm
2474  if(present(idrt)) idrt=gfile%idrt
2475  if(present(rlon_min)) rlon_min=gfile%rlon_min
2476  if(present(rlon_max)) rlon_max=gfile%rlon_max
2477  if(present(rlat_min)) rlat_min=gfile%rlat_min
2478  if(present(rlat_max)) rlat_max=gfile%rlat_max
2479  if(present(rlat_max)) rlat_max=gfile%rlat_max
2480  if(present(tlmeta)) tlmeta=gfile%tlmeta
2481  if(present(file_endian)) file_endian=gfile%file_endian
2482  if(present(do_byteswap)) do_byteswap=gfile%do_byteswap
2483  if(present(extrameta)) extrameta=gfile%extrameta
2484  if(present(flunit)) flunit=gfile%flunit
2485 !
2486 !--- rec
2487  if(present(recname) ) then
2488  if (gfile%nrec.ne.size(recname)) then
2489  if ( present(iret)) return
2490  call nemsio_stop
2491  else
2492  recname=gfile%recname
2493  endif
2494  endif
2495  if(present(reclevtyp)) then
2496  if (gfile%nrec.ne.size(reclevtyp)) then
2497  if ( present(iret)) return
2498  call nemsio_stop
2499  else
2500  reclevtyp=gfile%reclevtyp
2501  endif
2502  endif
2503  if(present(reclev) ) then
2504  if (gfile%nrec.ne.size(reclev)) then
2505  if ( present(iret)) return
2506  call nemsio_stop
2507  else
2508  reclev=gfile%reclev
2509  endif
2510  endif
2511 !--- vcoord
2512  if(present(vcoord)) then
2513  if (size(vcoord) .ne. (gfile%dimz+1)*2*3 ) then
2514  if ( present(iret)) return
2515  call nemsio_stop
2516  else
2517  vcoord=gfile%vcoord
2518  endif
2519  endif
2520 !--- lat
2521  if(present(lat) ) then
2522  if (size(lat).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2523  print *,'ERROR: size(lat)=',size(lat),' is not equal to ',gfile%fieldsize
2524  if ( present(iret)) return
2525  call nemsio_stop
2526  else
2527  lat=gfile%lat
2528  endif
2529  endif
2530 !--- lon
2531  if(present(lon) ) then
2532  if (size(lon).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2533  print *,'ERROR: size(lon)=',size(lon),' is not equal to ',gfile%fieldsize
2534  if ( present(iret)) return
2535  call nemsio_stop
2536  else
2537  lon=gfile%lon
2538  endif
2539  endif
2540 !--- dx
2541  if(present(dx) ) then
2542  if (size(dx).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2543  print *,'ERROR: size(dX)=',size(dx),' is not equal to ',gfile%fieldsize
2544  if ( present(iret)) return
2545  call nemsio_stop
2546  else
2547  dx=gfile%dx
2548  endif
2549  endif
2550 !--- dy
2551  if(present(dy) ) then
2552  if (size(dy).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
2553  print *,'ERROR: size(dy)=',size(dy),' is not equal to ',gfile%fieldsize
2554  if ( present(iret)) return
2555  call nemsio_stop
2556  else
2557  dy=gfile%dy
2558  endif
2559  endif
2560 !--- Cpi
2561  if(present(cpi) ) then
2562  if (gfile%ntrac+1.ne.size(cpi)) then
2563  if ( present(iret)) return
2564  call nemsio_stop
2565  else
2566  cpi=gfile%Cpi
2567  endif
2568  endif
2569 !--- Ri
2570  if(present(ri) ) then
2571  if (gfile%ntrac+1.ne.size(ri)) then
2572  if ( present(iret)) return
2573  call nemsio_stop
2574  else
2575  ri=gfile%Ri
2576  endif
2577  endif
2578 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2579 !*** for extra meta field
2580 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2581 !extrameta
2582  if(present(extrameta) ) extrameta=gfile%extrameta
2583  if (present(nmetavari) ) nmetavari=gfile%nmetavari
2584  if (present(nmetavarr) ) nmetavarr=gfile%nmetavarr
2585  if (present(nmetavarl) ) nmetavarl=gfile%nmetavarl
2586  if (present(nmetavarc) ) nmetavarc=gfile%nmetavarc
2587  if (present(nmetavarr8) ) nmetavarr8=gfile%nmetavarr8
2588  if (present(nmetaaryi) ) nmetaaryi=gfile%nmetaaryi
2589  if (present(nmetaaryr) ) nmetaaryr=gfile%nmetaaryr
2590  if (present(nmetaaryl) ) nmetaaryl=gfile%nmetaaryl
2591  if (present(nmetaaryc) ) nmetaaryc=gfile%nmetaaryc
2592  if (present(nmetaaryr8) ) nmetaaryr8=gfile%nmetaaryr8
2593  if ( gfile%nmetavari.gt.0 ) then
2594  if (present(variname)) then
2595  if( size(variname).eq.gfile%nmetavari) variname=gfile%variname
2596  endif
2597  if (present(varival)) then
2598  if(size(varival).eq.gfile%nmetavari) varival=gfile%varival
2599  endif
2600  endif
2601  if ( gfile%nmetavarr.gt.0 ) then
2602  if (present(varrname)) then
2603  if(size(varrname).eq.gfile%nmetavarr) varrname=gfile%varrname
2604  endif
2605  if (present(varrval)) then
2606  if(size(varrval).eq.gfile%nmetavarr) varrval=gfile%varrval
2607  endif
2608  endif
2609  if ( gfile%nmetavarl.gt.0 ) then
2610  if (present(varlname)) then
2611  if(size(varlname).eq.gfile%nmetavarl) varlname=gfile%varlname
2612  endif
2613  if (present(varlval)) then
2614  if(size(varlval).eq.gfile%nmetavarl) varlval=gfile%varlval
2615  endif
2616  endif
2617  if ( gfile%nmetavarc.gt.0 ) then
2618  if (present(varcname)) then
2619  if(size(varcname).eq.gfile%nmetavarc) varcname=gfile%varcname
2620  endif
2621  if (present(varcval)) then
2622  if(size(varcval).eq.gfile%nmetavarc) varcval=gfile%varcval
2623  endif
2624  endif
2625  if ( gfile%nmetavarr8.gt.0 ) then
2626  if (present(varr8name)) then
2627  if(size(varr8name).eq.gfile%nmetavarr8) varr8name=gfile%varr8name
2628  endif
2629  if (present(varr8val)) then
2630  if(size(varr8val).eq.gfile%nmetavarr8) varr8val=gfile%varr8val
2631  endif
2632  endif
2633  if ( gfile%nmetaaryi.gt.0 ) then
2634  if (present(aryiname)) then
2635  if(size(aryiname).eq.gfile%nmetaaryi) aryiname=gfile%aryiname
2636  endif
2637  if (present(aryilen)) then
2638  if(size(aryilen).eq.gfile%nmetaaryi) aryilen=gfile%aryilen
2639  endif
2640  if (present(aryival)) then
2641  if(size(aryival).eq.gfile%nmetaaryi*maxval(gfile%aryilen) ) &
2642  aryival=gfile%aryival
2643  endif
2644  endif
2645  if ( gfile%nmetaaryr.gt.0 ) then
2646  if (present(aryrname)) then
2647  if( size(aryrname).eq.gfile%nmetaaryr) aryrname=gfile%aryrname
2648  endif
2649  if (present(aryrlen)) then
2650  if(size(aryrlen).eq.gfile%nmetaaryr) aryrlen=gfile%aryrlen
2651  endif
2652  if (present(aryrval)) then
2653  if(size(aryrval).eq.gfile%nmetaaryr*maxval(gfile%aryrlen) ) &
2654  aryrval=gfile%aryrval
2655  endif
2656  endif
2657  if ( gfile%nmetaaryl.gt.0 ) then
2658  if (present(arylname)) then
2659  if(size(arylname).eq.gfile%nmetaaryl) arylname=gfile%arylname
2660  endif
2661  if (present(aryllen)) then
2662  if(size(aryllen).eq.gfile%nmetaaryl) aryllen=gfile%aryllen
2663  endif
2664  if (present(arylval)) then
2665  if(size(arylval).eq.gfile%nmetaaryl*maxval(gfile%aryllen) ) &
2666  arylval=gfile%arylval
2667  endif
2668  endif
2669  if ( gfile%nmetaaryc.gt.0 ) then
2670  if (present(arycname)) then
2671  if(size(arycname).eq.gfile%nmetaaryc) arycname=gfile%arycname
2672  endif
2673  if (present(aryclen)) then
2674  if(size(aryclen).eq.gfile%nmetaaryc) aryclen=gfile%aryclen
2675  endif
2676  if (present(arycval)) then
2677  if(size(arycval).eq.gfile%nmetaaryc*maxval(gfile%aryclen) ) &
2678  arycval=gfile%arycval
2679  endif
2680  endif
2681  if ( gfile%nmetaaryr8.gt.0 ) then
2682  if (present(aryr8name)) then
2683  if( size(aryr8name).eq.gfile%nmetaaryr8) aryr8name=gfile%aryr8name
2684  endif
2685  if (present(aryr8len)) then

2687  endif
2688  if (present(aryr8val)) then

2690  aryr8val=gfile%aryr8val
2691  endif
2692  endif

3018  subroutine nemsio_getrechead(gfile,jrec,name,levtyp,lev,iret)
3019 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3020 ! abstract: given record number, return users record name, lev typ, and levs
3021 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3022  implicit none
3023  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(in) :: gfile
3024  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(in) :: jrec
3025  character(*),intent(inout) :: name
3026  character(*),optional,intent(inout) :: levtyp
3027  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: lev
3028  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
3029  integer :: ios
3030 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
3031  if( present(iret)) iret=-11
3032  if ( jrec.gt.0 .or. jrec.le.gfile%nrec) then
3033  if(gfile%nmeta>2) then
3034  name=gfile%recname(jrec)
3035  else
3036  print *,'ERROR: recname is not specified in meta data!'
3037  return
3038  endif
3039  if(present(levtyp).and.gfile%nmeta>3) then
3040  levtyp=gfile%reclevtyp(jrec)
3041  endif
3042  if(present(lev).and.gfile%nmeta>4) then
3043  lev=gfile%reclev(jrec)
3044  endif
3045  if(present(iret)) iret=0
3046  return
3047  else
3048  if ( present(iret)) then
3049  print *,'ERROR: jrec is either less than 1 or greater than gfile%nrec'
3050  return
3051  else
3052  call nemsio_stop
3053  endif
3054  endif
3055  end subroutine nemsio_getrechead

3057 
3058  subroutine nemsio_gfinit(gfile,iret,recname,reclevtyp,reclev)
3059 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3060 ! abstract: set gfile variables to operational model output
3061 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3062  implicit none
3063  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
3064  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
3065  character(*),optional,intent(in) :: recname(:)
3066  character(*),optional,intent(in) :: reclevtyp(:)
3067  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: reclev(:)
3068  integer :: i,j,rec,rec3dopt
3069  real(nemsio_dblekind),allocatable :: slat(:),wlat(:)
3070  real(nemsio_dblekind),allocatable :: dx(:)
3071  real(nemsio_dblekind) :: radi
3072  logical(nemsio_logickind) :: linit=.false.,ltmp
3073 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
3074 ! set operational format
3075 !
3076  iret=-8
3077  if(gfile%version==nemsio_intfill) gfile%version=200809
3078  if(gfile%nfday==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nfday=0
3079  if(gfile%nfhour==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nfhour=0
3080  if(gfile%nfminute==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nfminute=0
3081  if(gfile%nfsecondn==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nfsecondn=0
3082  if(gfile%nfsecondd==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nfsecondd=100
3083  if(gfile%nmetavari==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetavari=0
3084  if(gfile%nmetavarr==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetavarr=0
3085  if(gfile%nmetavarc==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetavarc=0
3086  if(gfile%nmetavarl==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetavarl=0
3087  if(gfile%nmetaaryi==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetaaryi=0
3088  if(gfile%nmetaaryr==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetaaryr=0
3089  if(gfile%nmetaaryl==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetaaryl=0
3090  if(gfile%nmetaaryc==nemsio_intfill) gfile%nmetaaryc=0
3091 
3092 ! write(0,*)'in gfinit, modelname=',gfile%modelname
3093 
3094  linit=.false.
3095  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%modelname),'GFS')) then
3096  if(gfile%dimy.eq.nemsio_intfill) then
3097  linit=.true.
3098  gfile%dimy=576
3099  endif

3709 ! temporary subroutines for basio file unit
3710  subroutine nemsio_getlu(gfile,gfname,gaction,iret,ltlendian)
3711 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3712 ! abstract: set unit number to the first number available between 600-699
3713 ! according to unit number array fileunit
3714 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3715  implicit none
3716  type(nemsio_gfile),intent (inout) :: gfile
3717  character*(*),intent(in) :: gfname,gaction
3718  integer,intent(out) :: iret
3719  logical,optional,intent(in) :: ltlendian
3720  integer :: i
3721  logical :: flltlendian
3722  iret=-10
3723  gfile%gfname=gfname
3724  gfile%gaction=gaction
3725  flltlendian=.false.
3726  if(present(ltlendian))flltlendian=ltlendian
3727  if(.not. flltlendian) then
3728  do i=600,999
3729  if ( fileunit(i) .eq. 0 ) then
3730  gfile%flunit=i
3731  fileunit(i)=i
3732  iret=0
3733  exit
3734  endif
3735  enddo
3736  elseif(flltlendian) then
3737  do i=1300,1699
3738  if ( fileunit(i) .eq. 0 ) then
3739  gfile%flunit=i
3740  fileunit(i)=i
3741  iret=0
3742  exit
3743  endif
3744  enddo
3745  endif
3746  end subroutine nemsio_getlu
3747 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3748 ! temporary subroutines for free unit number
3749  subroutine nemsio_clslu(gfile,iret)
3750 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3751 ! abstract: free unit number array index corresponding to unit number
3752 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3753  implicit none
3754  type(nemsio_gfile),intent (inout) :: gfile
3755  integer, intent(out) :: iret
3756  iret=-10
3757  if ( fileunit(gfile%flunit) .ne. 0 ) then
3758  fileunit(gfile%flunit)=0
3759  gfile%flunit=0
3760  iret=0
3761  endif
3762  end subroutine nemsio_clslu

3764 !
3765  subroutine nemsio_setrqst(gfile,grbmeta,iret,jrec,vname,vlevtyp,vlev,w34,idrt, &
3766  itr,zhour,ibms,precision)
3767 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3768 ! abstract: if given record number, find record name, lev typ, and levs or
3769 ! record name,lev type and lev can be got from argument list.
3770 ! with record name,lev typ and level, set up grib meta, jpds and
3771 ! jgds
3772 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3773  implicit none
3774  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
3775  type(nemsio_grbmeta),intent(out) :: grbmeta
3776  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: jrec
3777  character(*),optional,intent(in) :: vname,vlevtyp
3778  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: vlev
3779  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
3780  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: w34
3781  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: idrt
3782  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: itr
3783  real(nemsio_realkind),optional,intent(in) :: zhour
3784  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: ibms
3785  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: precision
3786  character(255) :: name,levtyp
3787  integer :: icen,iptv,itl,jbms,jftu,jp1,jp2,jtr,jna,jnm,ios
3788  integer :: i,lev,ktbl,krec,idrt_in,itr_rw
3789 !------------------------------------------------------------
3790 ! with record number, find record name, level type and level
3791 !------------------------------------------------------------
3792  iret=-5
3793  if ( present(jrec)) then
3794  if ( jrec.gt.0 .and. jrec.le.gfile%nrec) then
3795  name=gfile%recname(jrec)
3796  levtyp=gfile%reclevtyp(jrec)
3797  lev=gfile%reclev(jrec)
3798  else
3799  return
3800  endif
3801  elseif ( present(vname) .and. present(vlevtyp) .and. present(vlev)) then
3802  name=trim(vname)
3803  levtyp=trim(vlevtyp)
3804  lev=vlev
3805  else
3806  return
3807  endif
3808 ! write(0,*)'in setrqst,name=',trim(name),trim(levtyp),lev,'jrec=',jrec
3809 !------------------------------------------------------------
3810 ! find index in grib table according to recname and reclevtyp
3811 !------------------------------------------------------------
3812  call nemsio_grbtbl_search(trim(name),trim(levtyp),ktbl,krec,ios)
3813  if(ios.ne.0) return
3814 
3815 !*** lev: for special layer
3816 ! if ( gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%leveltype .eq.'sfc' ) then
3817  if ( trim(gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%leveltype) .ne.'layer' .and. &
3818  trim(gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%leveltype) .ne.'mid layer' ) then
3819  lev=0
3820  endif
3821 ! write(0,*)'in searchrst,jrec=',jrec,'name=',trim(name),'levtyp=',trim(levtyp),&
3822 ! 'lev=',lev,'gribtb levtype=',gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%leveltype
3823 !------------------------------------------------------------
3824 ! for read, just need to set up jpds(05-07)
3825 !------------------------------------------------------------
3826 !--- read:set jpds5,6,7
3827 ! if ( lowercase(gfile%gaction)(1:4).eq."read") then
3828  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),"read") .or. &
3829  equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%gaction),"rdwr") ) then
3830  grbmeta%jpds(05)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1param
3831  grbmeta%jpds(06)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1level
3832  grbmeta%jpds(07)=lev
3833  if ( grbmeta%jpds(06).eq.110 ) then
3834  grbmeta%jpds(07)=256*(lev-1)+lev
3835  endif
3836  if (gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1lev.ne.0) then
3837  grbmeta%jpds(07)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1lev
3838  endif
3839 !
3840  itr_rw=10
3841  if(index(trim(name),"_ave")>0) itr_rw=3
3842  if(index(trim(name),"_acc")>0) itr_rw=4
3843  if(index(trim(name),"_max")>0) itr_rw=2
3844  if(index(trim(name),"_min")>0) itr_rw=2
3845  else
3846 !------------------------------------------------------------
3847 ! for write, need to set up jgds(1:25), jpds(01-20)
3848 !------------------------------------------------------------
3849  if (present(precision)) then
3850  gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%precision=precision
3851  endif
3852  if (present(idrt)) then
3853  idrt_in = idrt
3854  else
3855 !*** gfile idrt
3856  idrt_in=gfile%idrt
3857  endif
3858 !*** for itr
3859  jftu=1
3860  jtr=10
3861  jp1=gfile%nfhour
3862  jp2=0
3863  if(present(itr) ) then
3864  jtr=itr
3865  if(itr==3.or.itr==2.or.itr==4) then !avg
3866  if(present(zhour)) then
3867  jp1=nint(zhour)
3868  jp2=gfile%nfhour
3869  else
3870  print *,'ERROR in nemsio gribfile,itr=',itr,'need to set zhour'
3871  endif
3872  endif
3873  endif
3874  itr_rw=jtr
3875  jbms=0
3876  if(present(ibms)) jbms=ibms
3877 !
3878  icen=7
3879 !
3880  if(maxval(gfile%jgds)==nemsio_kpds_intfill.and. &
3881  minval(gfile%jgds)==nemsio_kpds_intfill ) then
3882  if ( present(w34) ) then
3883  call nemsio_makglgds(gfile,idrt_in,grbmeta%jgds,ios,w34)
3884  gfile%jgds=grbmeta%jgds
3885  else
3886  call nemsio_makglgds(gfile,idrt_in,grbmeta%jgds,ios)
3887  gfile%jgds=grbmeta%jgds
3888 ! write(0,*)'after nemsio_makglgds,idrt=',idrt_in,'ios=',ios, &
3889 ! 'jbms=',jbms
3890  endif
3891  else
3892  grbmeta%jgds=gfile%jgds
3893  endif
3894  if(ios.ne.0) return
3895  iptv=gribtable(ktbl)%iptv
3896 ! itl=1
3897  jna=0
3898  jnm=0
3899  call nemsio_makglpds(gfile,iptv,icen,jbms,&
3900  jftu,jp1,jp2,itr_rw,jna,jnm,jrec,ktbl,krec,lev,grbmeta%jpds,ios)
3901 ! write(0,*)'after nemsio_makglpds,jpds=',grbmeta%jpds(1:25),'ios=',ios, &
3902 ! 'lev=',lev
3903  if(ios.ne.0) return
3904  endif
3905 !------------------------------------------------------------
3906 ! set up grib meta lbms
3907 !------------------------------------------------------------
3908  grbmeta%jf=gfile%fieldsize
3909  allocate(grbmeta%lbms(grbmeta%jf))
3910  iret=0
3911  end subroutine nemsio_setrqst
3912 
3913  subroutine nemsio_makglgds(gfile,idrt,kgds,iret,w34)
3914 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3915 ! abstract: set up gds for grib meta
3916 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3917  implicit none
3918  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
3919  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
3920  integer,intent(in):: idrt
3921  integer,optional,intent(in):: w34
3922  integer,intent(out):: kgds(200)
3923  real(nemsio_dblekind) :: slat8(gfile%dimy)
3924  real(nemsio_realkind) :: slat4(gfile%dimy)
3925  integer :: n,igrid
3926 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
3927  iret=-5
3928  igrid=255
3929  if(idrt.eq.0.and.gfile%dimx.eq.144.and.gfile%dimy.eq.73) igrid=2
3930  if(idrt.eq.0.and.gfile%dimx.eq.360.and.gfile%dimy.eq.181) igrid=3
3931  if(idrt.eq.0.and.gfile%dimx.eq.720.and.gfile%dimy.eq.361) igrid=4
3932  if(idrt.eq.4.and.gfile%dimx.eq.192.and.gfile%dimy.eq.94) igrid=98
3933  if(idrt.eq.4.and.gfile%dimx.eq.384.and.gfile%dimy.eq.192) igrid=126
3934  if(idrt.eq.4.and.gfile%dimx.eq.512.and.gfile%dimy.eq.256) igrid=170
3935  if(idrt.eq.4.and.gfile%dimx.eq.768.and.gfile%dimy.eq.384) igrid=127
3936  gfile%igrid=igrid
3937 ! write(0,*)'in nemsio_makdglgds,idrt=',idrt,'dimx=',gfile%dimx,'dimy=',gfile%dimy
3938  kgds(1)=modulo(idrt,256)
3939  kgds(2)=gfile%dimx
3940  kgds(3)=gfile%dimy
3941  select case(idrt)
3942  case(0)
3943  kgds(4)=90000
3944  case(4)
3945 !------------------------------------------------------------
3946 ! call different split for w3_4 lib and w3_d lib
3947 !------------------------------------------------------------
3948  if (present (w34)) then
3949  call splat(idrt,gfile%dimy,slat4)
3950  kgds(4)=nint(180000./acos(-1.)*asin(slat4(1)))
3951  else
3952  call splat(idrt,gfile%dimy,slat8)
3953  kgds(4)=nint(180000./acos(-1.)*asin(slat8(1)))
3954  endif
3955  case(256)
3956  kgds(4)=90000-nint(0.5*180000./gfile%dimy)
3957  end select
3958  kgds(5)=0
3959  kgds(6)=128
3960  kgds(7)=-kgds(4)
3961  kgds(8)=-nint(360000./gfile%dimx)
3962  kgds(9)=-kgds(8)
3963  select case(idrt)
3964  case(0)
3965  kgds(10)=nint(180000./(gfile%dimy-1))
3966  case(4)
3967  kgds(10)=gfile%dimy/2
3968  case(256)
3969  kgds(10)=nint(180000./gfile%dimy)
3970  end select
3971  kgds(11)=0
3972  kgds(12)=0
3973  kgds(13:18)=-1
3974  kgds(19)=0
3975  kgds(20)=255
3976  kgds(21:)=-1
3977  iret=0
3978  end subroutine nemsio_makglgds
3979 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3980  subroutine nemsio_makglpds(gfile,iptv,icen,ibms,&
3981  iftu,ip1,ip2,itr,ina,inm,jrec,ktbl,krec,lev,kpds,iret)
3982 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3983 ! abstract: set up gps for grib meta
3984 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
3985  implicit none
3986  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(in) :: gfile
3987  integer,intent(in):: iptv,icen,ibms
3988  integer,intent(in):: iftu,ip1,ip2,itr,ina,inm,jrec,ktbl,krec,lev
3989  integer,intent(out):: kpds(200)
3990  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
3991  integer :: i,igen,icen2,igrid
3992 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
3993  iret=-5
3994 !
3995 !igrid
3996  igrid=gfile%igrid
3997 !get igen icen2
3998  call nemsio_getheadvar(gfile,'igen',igen,iret)
3999  if (iret.ne.0 ) then
4000  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%modelname),'GFS')) then
4001  igen=82
4002  else
4003  print *,'ERROR: please specify model generating flag'
4004  return
4005  endif
4006  endif
4007  call nemsio_getheadvar(gfile,'icen2',icen2,iret)
4008  if (iret.ne.0 ) then
4009  if(equal_str_nocase(trim(gfile%modelname),'GFS')) then
4010  icen2=0
4011  else
4012  print *,'ERROR: please specify subcenter id,modelname=',gfile%modelname
4013  return
4014  endif
4015  endif
4016 !
4017  kpds(01)=icen
4018  kpds(02)=igen
4019  kpds(03)=igrid
4020  kpds(04)=128+64*ibms
4021  kpds(05)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1param
4022  kpds(06)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1level
4023  kpds(07)=lev
4024  if(gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1lev/=0)then
4025  kpds(07)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%g1lev
4026  endif
4027 !*** deal with dpres
4028  if ( kpds(06).eq.110 ) then
4029  kpds(07)=256*(lev-1)+lev
4030  endif
4031 !***
4032  kpds(08)=mod(gfile%idate(1)-1,100)+1
4033  kpds(09)=gfile%idate(2)
4034  kpds(10)=gfile%idate(3)
4035  kpds(11)=gfile%idate(4)
4036  kpds(12)=0
4037  kpds(13)=iftu
4038  kpds(14)=ip1
4039  kpds(15)=ip2
4040  kpds(16)=itr
4041  kpds(17)=ina
4042  kpds(18)=1
4043  kpds(19)=iptv
4044  kpds(20)=inm
4045  kpds(21)=(gfile%idate(1)-1)/100+1
4046  kpds(22)=gribtable(ktbl)%item(krec)%precision
4047  kpds(23)=icen2
4048  kpds(24)=0
4049  kpds(25)=0
4050  kpds(26:)=-1
4051  iret=0
4052 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
4053  end subroutine nemsio_makglpds
4054 !
4055 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4056  subroutine nemsio_searchrecv(gfile,jrec,name,levtyp,lev,iret)
4057 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4058 ! abstract: search rec number giving rec name, levtyp and lev
4059 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4060  implicit none
4061  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(in) :: gfile
4062  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: jrec
4063  character(*),intent(in) :: name
4064  character(*),intent(in),optional :: levtyp
4065  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(in) :: lev
4066  integer(nemsio_intkind),optional,intent(out) :: iret
4067  integer i, nsize,nlen,nlen1
4068 
4069 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4070  iret=-5
4071  nlen=min(len(name),len(gfile%recname))
4072  nlen1=min(len(levtyp),len(gfile%reclevtyp))
4073 !
4074  jrec=0
4075  if(size(gfile%recname)/=gfile%nrec) return
4076  if(.not.present(levtyp)) then
4077  do i=1,gfile%nrec
4078  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(name),trim(gfile%recname(i))) ) then
4079  jrec=i
4080  exit
4081  endif
4082  enddo
4083  else if (size(gfile%reclevtyp).eq.gfile%nrec) then
4084  if(.not.present(lev)) then
4085  do i=1,gfile%nrec
4086  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(name),trim(gfile%recname(i))) .and. &
4087  equal_str_nocase(trim(levtyp),trim(gfile%reclevtyp(i))) ) then
4088  jrec=i
4089  exit
4090  endif
4091  enddo
4092  else if(size(gfile%reclev).eq.gfile%nrec) then
4093  do i=1,gfile%nrec
4094  if ( equal_str_nocase(trim(name),trim(gfile%recname(i))) .and. &
4095  equal_str_nocase(trim(levtyp),trim(gfile%reclevtyp(i)) ) .and. &
4096  lev==gfile%reclev(i) ) then
4097  jrec=i
4098  exit
4099  endif
4100  enddo
4101  endif
4102  endif
4103  if ( jrec .ne.0 ) iret=0
4104 !
4105  return
4106  end subroutine nemsio_searchrecv
4107 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4108 !
4109 !----------------------------------------------------------------------------
4110  subroutine nemsio_grbtbl_search(vname,vlevtyp,ktbl,krec,iret)
4111 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4112 ! abstract: given record name, levtyp and index number in grib table
4113 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4114  implicit none
4115  character(*),intent(in) :: vname,vlevtyp
4116  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: ktbl,krec
4117  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
4118  integer :: i,j
4119  character(16) :: lcname,lclevtyp
4120 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
4121  iret=-5
4122  i=0
4123  i=index(trim(vname),"_")
4124  lcname=trim(lowercase(trim(vname)))
4125  if(i>0) lcname=trim(lowercase(trim(vname(1:i-1))))
4126  lclevtyp=trim(lowercase(trim(vlevtyp)))
4127  ktbl=0
4128  krec=0
4129 ! write(0,*)'in nemsio vname=',vname,' vlevtyp=',vlevtyp,' lcname=',trim(lcname),i
4130  do j=1,size(gribtable)
4131  do i=1,size(gribtable(j)%item)
4132  if(trim(gribtable(j)%item(i)%shortname)==trim(lcname) .and. &
4133  trim(gribtable(j)%item(i)%leveltype)==trim(lclevtyp) )then
4134  ktbl=j
4135  krec=i
4136  iret=0
4137  exit
4138  endif
4139  enddo
4140  enddo
4141 ! write(0,*)'in grbtbl_search,krec=',krec,'ktbl=',ktbl,'krec=',krec
4142  end subroutine nemsio_grbtbl_search
4143 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4144  subroutine nemsio_chkgfary(gfile,iret)
4145 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4146 ! abstract: check if arrays in gfile is allocated and with right size
4147 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4148  implicit none
4149  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
4150  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
4151  integer :: ios
4152 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
4153  iret=-2
4154  if ( gfile%dimx .eq. nemsio_intfill .or. gfile%dimy .eq. nemsio_intfill &
4155  .or. gfile%dimz .eq. nemsio_intfill .or. gfile%nrec .eq. nemsio_intfill ) then
4156  print *,'ERROR: dimx,dimy,dimz and nrec must be defined!'
4157  return
4158  endif
4159  if(gfile%nmeta>5) then
4160  if (.not. allocated(gfile%vcoord) .or. size(gfile%vcoord).ne. &
4161  (gfile%dimz+1)*3*2 ) then
4162  call nemsio_almeta1(gfile,ios)
4163  if (ios .ne. 0) return
4164  endif
4165  endif
4166  if(gfile%nmeta>=10) then
4167  if (.not.allocated(gfile%lat) .or. size(gfile%lat).ne.gfile%fieldsize .or.&
4168  .not.allocated(gfile%lon) .or. size(gfile%lon).ne.gfile%fieldsize .or.&
4169  .not.allocated(gfile%dx) .or. size(gfile%dx).ne.gfile%fieldsize .or.&
4170  .not.allocated(gfile%dy) .or. size(gfile%dy).ne.gfile%fieldsize) then
4171  call nemsio_almeta2(gfile,ios)
4172  if (ios .ne. 0) return
4173  endif
4174  endif
4175  if(gfile%nmeta>=12) then
4176  if(gfile%ntrac==nemsio_intfill) then
4177  print *,'ERROR: ntrac is not defined!'
4178  return
4179  endif
4180  if (.not.allocated(gfile%Cpi) .or. size(gfile%Cpi).ne.gfile%ntrac+1 .or. &
4181  .not.allocated(gfile%Ri) .or. size(gfile%Ri).ne.gfile%ntrac+1 ) then
4182  call nemsio_almeta3(gfile,ios)
4183  if (ios .ne. 0) return
4184  endif
4185  endif
4186 
4187  if(gfile%nmeta>2) then
4188  if (allocated(gfile%recname) .and. size(gfile%recname).eq.gfile%nrec)&
4189  then
4190  if (allocated(gfile%reclevtyp) .and. size(gfile%reclevtyp) &
4191  .eq.gfile%nrec) then
4192  if (allocated(gfile%reclev) .and. size(gfile%reclev).eq. &
4193  gfile%nrec) then
4194  iret=0
4195  return
4196  endif
4197  endif
4198  endif
4199 
4200  call nemsio_almeta4(gfile,ios)
4201  if (ios .ne. 0) return
4202  endif
4203  iret=0
4204  end subroutine nemsio_chkgfary
4205 !------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4206  subroutine nemsio_almeta(gfile,iret)
4207 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4208 ! abstract: allocate all the arrays in gfile
4209 !- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -- - - - - - - -
4210  implicit none
4211  type(nemsio_gfile),intent(inout) :: gfile
4212  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(out) :: iret
4213  integer ::dimvcoord1,dimvcoord2,dimnmmlev
4214  integer ::dimrecname,dimreclevtyp,dimreclev
4215  integer ::dimfield
4216  integer ::dimcpr
4217  integer ::iret1,iret2,iret3,iret4,iret5
4218 ! - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
4219  iret=0
4220  dimvcoord1=gfile%dimz+1
4221  dimrecname=gfile%nrec
4222  dimreclevtyp=gfile%nrec
4223  dimreclev=gfile%nrec
4224  dimfield=gfile%fieldsize
4225  dimcpr=gfile%ntrac+1
4226  if(allocated(gfile%recname)) deallocate(gfile%recname)
4227  if(allocated(gfile%reclevtyp)) deallocate(gfile%reclevtyp)
4228  if(allocated(gfile%reclev)) deallocate(gfile%reclev)
4229  if(allocated(gfile%vcoord)) deallocate(gfile%vcoord)
4230  if(allocated(gfile%lat)) deallocate(gfile%lat)
4231  if(allocated(gfile%lon)) deallocate(gfile%lon)
4232  if(allocated(gfile%dx)) deallocate(gfile%dx)
4233  if(allocated(gfile%dy)) deallocate(gfile%dy)
4234  if(allocated(gfile%Cpi)) deallocate(gfile%Cpi)
4235  if(allocated(gfile%Ri)) deallocate(gfile%Ri)
4236  if(gfile%nmeta>=5)then
4237  allocate(gfile%recname(dimrecname), gfile%reclevtyp(dimreclevtyp), &
4238  gfile%reclev(dimreclev), &
4239  stat=iret1)
4240  if(iret1.eq.0) then
4241  gfile%reclev=nemsio_intfill
4242  gfile%recname=' '
4243  gfile%reclevtyp=' '
4244  endif
4245  iret=iret+abs(iret1)
4246  endif
4247  if(gfile%nmeta>=6)then
4248  allocate(gfile%vcoord(dimvcoord1,3,2) ,stat=iret2)
4249  if(iret2.eq.0) then
4250  gfile%vcoord=nemsio_realfill
4251  endif
4252  iret=iret+abs(iret2)
4253  endif
4254  if(gfile%nmeta>=8)then
4255  allocate(gfile%lat(dimfield), gfile%lon(dimfield),stat=iret3)
4256  if(iret3.eq.0) then
4257  gfile%lat=nemsio_realfill
4258  gfile%lon=nemsio_realfill
4259  endif
4260  iret=iret+abs(iret3)
4261  endif
4262  if(gfile%nmeta>=10)then
4263  allocate(gfile%dx(dimfield), gfile%dy(dimfield) ,stat=iret4)
4264  if(iret4.eq.0) then
4265  gfile%dx=nemsio_realfill
4266  gfile%dy=nemsio_realfill
4267  endif
4268  iret=iret+abs(iret4)
4269  endif
4270  if(gfile%nmeta>=12)then
4271  allocate(gfile%Cpi(dimcpr), gfile%Ri(dimcpr), stat=iret5)
4272  if(iret5.eq.0) then
4273  gfile%Cpi=nemsio_realfill
4274  gfile%Ri=nemsio_realfill
4275  endif
4276  iret=iret+abs(iret5)
4277  endif
4278 
4279  if(iret.ne.0) iret=-6
4280  end subroutine nemsio_almeta

4610  iret=-17

4741  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headaryiname)) then

4749  endif
4750  endif
4751 !
4752 !--- gfile%head real ary
4753  if(gfile%headaryrnum>0) then
4754  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headaryrname)) allocate(gfile%headaryrname(gfile%headaryrnum) )
4755  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headaryrval)) &
4756  allocate(gfile%headaryrval(max(gfile%fieldsize,(gfile%dimz+1)*6),gfile%headaryrnum))
4757  gfile%headaryrname(1)='vcoord'

4759  do i=1,3
4760  do k=1,gfile%dimz+1
4761  gfile%headaryrval(k+((j-1)*3+i-1)*(gfile%dimz+1),1)=gfile%vcoord(k,i,j)
4762  enddo
4763  enddo
4764  enddo

4767  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%lat),2)=gfile%lat
4768  endif

4770  gfile%headaryrname(3)='lon'
4771  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%lon),3)=gfile%lon
4772  endif

4774  gfile%headaryrname(4)='dx'
4775  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%dx),4)=gfile%dx
4776  endif

4778  gfile%headaryrname(5)='dy'
4779  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%dy),5)=gfile%dy
4780  endif

4782  gfile%headaryrname(6)='cpi'
4783  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%cpi),6)=gfile%cpi
4784  endif

4787  gfile%headaryrval(1:size(gfile%ri),7)=gfile%ri
4788  endif
4789  endif
4790 !

4792  if(gfile%headarycnum >0) then
4793  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headarycname)) allocate(gfile%headarycname(gfile%headarycnum) )
4794  if(.not.allocated(gfile%headarycval)) allocate(gfile%headarycval(size(gfile%recname),gfile%headarycnum))
4795  gfile%headarycname(1)='recname'
4796  gfile%headarycval(1:size(gfile%recname),1)=gfile%recname
4797  if(gfile%headarycnum >1) then
4798  gfile%headarycname(2)='reclevtyp'
4799  gfile%headarycval(1:size(gfile%reclevtyp),2)=gfile%reclevtyp
4800  endif
4801  endif
4802 !
4803  iret=0
4804  end subroutine nemsio_setfhead

5148  SUBROUTINE nemsio_splat4(IDRT,JMAX,ASLAT)
5149 !$$$
5150  implicit none
5151  integer(nemsio_intkind),intent(in) :: idrt,jmax
5152  real(4),intent(out) :: ASLAT(JMAX)
5153  INTEGER(nemsio_intkind),PARAMETER:: KD=selected_real_kind(15,45)
5154  REAL(KIND=kd):: pk(jmax/2),pkm1(jmax/2),pkm2(jmax/2)
5155  REAL(KIND=kd):: aslatd(jmax/2),sp,spmax,eps=10.d0*epsilon(sp)
5156  integer,PARAMETER:: JZ=50
5157  REAL(nemsio_dblekind) BZ(JZ)
5158  DATA bz / 2.4048255577d0, 5.5200781103d0, &
5159  8.6537279129d0, 11.7915344391d0, 14.9309177086d0, 18.0710639679d0, &
5160  21.2116366299d0, 24.3524715308d0, 27.4934791320d0, 30.6346064684d0, &
5161  33.7758202136d0, 36.9170983537d0, 40.0584257646d0, 43.1997917132d0, &
5162  46.3411883717d0, 49.4826098974d0, 52.6240518411d0, 55.7655107550d0, &
5163  58.9069839261d0, 62.0484691902d0, 65.1899648002d0, 68.3314693299d0, &
5164  71.4729816036d0, 74.6145006437d0, 77.7560256304d0, 80.8975558711d0, &
5165  84.0390907769d0, 87.1806298436d0, 90.3221726372d0, 93.4637187819d0, &
5166  96.6052679510d0, 99.7468198587d0, 102.888374254d0, 106.029930916d0, &
5167  109.171489649d0, 112.313050280d0, 115.454612653d0, 118.596176630d0, &
5168  121.737742088d0, 124.879308913d0, 128.020877005d0, 131.162446275d0, &
5169  134.304016638d0, 137.445588020d0, 140.587160352d0, 143.728733573d0, &
5170  146.870307625d0, 150.011882457d0, 153.153458019d0, 156.295034268d0 /
5171  REAL(8):: DLT,D1=1.d0
5172  INTEGER(4):: JHE,JHO,J0=0
5173  real(8),PARAMETER :: PI=3.14159265358979d0,c=(1.d0-(2.d0/pi)**2)*0.25d0
5174  real(8) r
5175  integer jh,js,n,j
5176 !C - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
5177 !C GAUSSIAN LATITUDES
5178  IF(idrt.EQ.4) THEN
5179  jh=jmax/2
5180  jhe=(jmax+1)/2
5181  r=1.d0/sqrt((jmax+0.5d0)**2+c)
5182  DO j=1,min(jh,jz)
5183  aslatd(j)=cos(bz(j)*r)
5184  ENDDO
5185  DO j=jz+1,jh
5186  aslatd(j)=cos((bz(jz)+(j-jz)*pi)*r)
5187  ENDDO
5188  spmax=1.d0
5189  DO WHILE(spmax.GT.eps)
5190  spmax=0.d0
5191  DO j=1,jh
5192  pkm1(j)=1.d0
5193  pk(j)=aslatd(j)
5194  ENDDO
5195  DO n=2,jmax
5196  DO j=1,jh
5197  pkm2(j)=pkm1(j)
5198  pkm1(j)=pk(j)
5199  pk(j)=((2*n-1)*aslatd(j)*pkm1(j)-(n-1)*pkm2(j))/n
5200  ENDDO
5201  ENDDO
5202  DO j=1,jh
5203  sp=pk(j)*(1.d0-aslatd(j)**2)/(jmax*(pkm1(j)-aslatd(j)*pk(j)))
5204  aslatd(j)=aslatd(j)-sp
5205  spmax=max(spmax,abs(sp))
5206  ENDDO
5207  ENDDO
5208 !CDIR$ IVDEP
5209  DO j=1,jh
5210  aslat(j)=aslatd(j)
5211  aslat(jmax+1-j)=-aslat(j)
5212  ENDDO
5213  IF(jhe.GT.jh) THEN
5214  aslat(jhe)=0.d0
5215  ENDIF
5216 !C - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
5217 !C EQUALLY-SPACED LATITUDES INCLUDING POLES
5218  ELSEIF(idrt.EQ.0) THEN
5219  jh=jmax/2
5220  jhe=(jmax+1)/2
5221  jho=jhe-1
5222  dlt=pi/(jmax-1)
5223  aslat(1)=1.d0
5224  DO j=2,jh
5225  aslat(j)=cos((j-1)*dlt)
5226  ENDDO
5227 !CDIR$ IVDEP
5228  DO j=1,jh
5229  aslat(jmax+1-j)=-aslat(j)
5230  ENDDO
5231  IF(jhe.GT.jh) THEN
5232  aslat(jhe)=0.d0
5233  ENDIF
5234 !C - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
5235 !C EQUALLY-SPACED LATITUDES EXCLUDING POLES
5236  ELSEIF(idrt.EQ.256) THEN
5237  jh=jmax/2
5238  jhe=(jmax+1)/2
5239  jho=jhe
5240  dlt=pi/jmax
5241  aslat(1)=1.d0
5242  DO j=1,jh
5243  aslat(j)=cos((j-0.5)*dlt)
5244  ENDDO
5245 !CDIR$ IVDEP
5246  DO j=1,jh
5247  aslat(jmax+1-j)=-aslat(j)
5248  ENDDO
5249  IF(jhe.GT.jh) THEN
5250  aslat(jhe)=0.d0
5251  ENDIF
5252  ENDIF
5253 !C - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
5254  end subroutine nemsio_splat4

5365  elemental function lowercase(word)
5366 !
5367 !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
5368 !
5369 ! convert a word to lower case
5370 !
5371  Character (len=32) :: lowercase
5372  Character (len=*) , intent(in) :: word
5373  integer :: i,ic,nlen
5374  nlen = len(word)
5375  if(nlen >32) then
5376  nlen=32
5377  endif
5378  lowercase(1:nlen)=word(1:nlen)
5379  do i=1,nlen
5380  ic = ichar(word(i:i))
5381  if (ic >= 65 .and. ic < 91) lowercase(i:i) = char(ic+32)
5382  end do
5383  if(nlen<32) lowercase(nlen+1:)=' '
5384 !
5385 !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
5386 !
5387  end function lowercase
5388 !
5389  elemental function equal_str_nocase(str1,str2)
5390 !
5391 !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
5392 !
5393 ! convert a word to lower case
5394 !
5395  logical :: equal_str_nocase
5396  Character (len=*) , intent(in) :: str1
5397  Character (len=*) , intent(in) :: str2
5398  integer :: i,ic1,ic2,nlen
5399  nlen = len(str2)
5400 !
5401  if(len(str1)/=nlen) then
5402  equal_str_nocase=.false.
5403  return
5404  endif
5405  equal_str_nocase=.false.
5406  do i=1,nlen
5407  ic1 = ichar(str1(i:i))
5408  if (ic1 >= 65 .and. ic1 < 91) ic1 = ic1+32
5409  ic2 = ichar(str2(i:i))
5410  if (ic2 >= 65 .and. ic2 < 91) ic2 = ic2+32
5411  if(ic1/=ic2) then
5412  equal_str_nocase=.false.
5413  return
5414  endif
5415  end do
5416  equal_str_nocase=.true.
5417 !
5418 !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
5419 !
5420  end function equal_str_nocase
